(65, 2, 'Xiaomi 15 Series in hand: Luxurious, soft design, powerful configuration with Snapdragon 8 Elite', '<h2>On October 29, 2024, Xiaomi launched the Xiaomi 15 Series with a few design tweaks and strong configuration upgrades compared to the Xiaomi 14 Series. With me <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/tren-tay-xiaomi-15-series-1571703\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"on hand Xiaomi 15 Series\">Xiaomi 15 Series in hand</a> see the model line <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"phone\">what&#39;s interesting about this phone</a>.</h2>', '<h3><strong>Hands on Xiaomi 15 Series with luxurious design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Overall, the Xiaomi 15 Series is designed based on a square outer frame and is finished from metal to bring a luxurious, sturdy feeling when looking at it. The company has also redesigned the curved outer frame to be softer than before to provide a comfortable holding experience for users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được thiết kế với kiểu dáng vuông vức quen thuộc. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-thiet-ke.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-thiet-ke.jpg\" title=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được thiết kế với kiểu dáng vuông vức quen thuộc. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xiaomi 15 Series is designed with a familiar square design. Source: Gizmochina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The backs of the Xiaomi 15 and Xiaomi 15 Pro duo are both flat and protected by rough tempered glass. This helps the product limit sweat and annoying fingerprints.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được trang bị mặt lưng kính nhám. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaom-15-series-mat-lung.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaom-15-series-mat-lung.jpg\" title=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được trang bị mặt lưng kính nhám. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xiaomi 15 Series is equipped with a matte glass back. Source: Gizmochina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prominent on the back of the Xiaomi 15 Series is the large square camera cluster located on the left. Different from the frame style like the Xiaomi 14 Series, the Xiaomi 15 series is curved more seamlessly with the back. This type of design makes the overall product more seamless and harmonious than before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cụm camera Xiaomi 15 Series dược thiết kế liền mạch hơn so với thế hệ trước. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xioami-15-series-camera.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xioami-15-series-camera.jpg\" title=\"Cụm camera Xiaomi 15 Series dược thiết kế liền mạch hơn so với thế hệ trước. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Xiaomi 15 Series camera cluster is designed more seamlessly than the previous generation. Source: Gizmochina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the front, Xiaomi 15 is equipped with a flat screen, measuring 6.36 inches. The Xiaomi 15 Pro is equipped with a large flat screen (6.78 inches) that is slightly curved on all four sides. Both of these products have very thin screen borders so they can provide good display space for users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được trang bị màn hình có viền mỏng. Nguồn; Gizmochina.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-man-hinh.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-man-hinh.jpg\" title=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được trang bị màn hình có viền mỏng. Nguồn; Gizmochina.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xiaomi 15 Series is equipped with a screen with 4 thin screen borders. Source: Gizmochina.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Xiaomi 15 Series configuration</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I will summarize all configuration parameters of Xiaomi 15 Series:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xiaomi 15:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen: Size 6.36 inches, LTPO OLED, 2,670 x 1,200 pixels, 120 Hz, maximum brightness 3,200 nits.</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite.</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 12 GB/16 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal memory: 256 GB/512 GB/1 TB.</li>\r\n	<li>Rear camera: 50 MP f/1.62 (main camera) + 50 MP f/2.0 (telephoto camera) + 50 MP f/2.2 (super wide-angle camera).</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera: 32 MP (aperture unknown).</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 5,400 mAh, supports 90 W wired fast charging, 50 W wireless fast charging.</li>\r\n	<li>Operating system: Xiaomi HyperOS 2.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xiaomi 15 Pro:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen: Size 6.73 inches, LTPO AMOLED panel, 3,200 x 1,440 pixels, scan frequency 1 - 120 Hz, maximum screen brightness 3,200 nits.</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite.</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 12 GB/16 GB.</li>\r\n	<li>Internal memory: 256 GB/512 GB/1 TB.</li>\r\n	<li>Rear camera: 50 MP, f/1.44 (main camera) + 50 MP, f/2.5 (Leica Periscope telephoto camera) + 50 MP, f/2.2 (super wide-angle camera).</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera: 32 MP.</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 6,100 mAh, 90 W wired fast charging, 50 W wireless fast charging.</li>\r\n	<li>Operating system: Xiaomi HyperOS 2.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>As everyone can see above, Xiaomi 15 Series is equipped with Qualcomm&#39;s high-end Snapdragon 8 Elite chip. This is Qualcomm&#39;s most powerful processor chip today, so the device&#39;s performance can meet most users&#39; needs. In particular, with Snapdragon 8 Elite, Xiaomi 15 Series can perform AI tasks more effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cả 2 sản phẩm mới nhà Xiaomi đều được trang bị chip Snapdragon 8 Elite cao cấp của Qualcomm. Nguồn: Qualcomm.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/snapdragon-8-elite-1729525996711.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/snapdragon-8-elite-1729525996711.jpg\" title=\"Cả 2 sản phẩm mới nhà Xiaomi đều được trang bị chip Snapdragon 8 Elite cao cấp của Qualcomm. Nguồn: Qualcomm.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Both new Xiaomi products are equipped with Qualcomm&#39;s high-end Snapdragon 8 Elite chip. Source: Qualcomm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xiaomi 15 and Xiaomi 15 Pro are both equipped with large batteries compared to the current 5,000 mAh. This is because Xiaomi has applied modern Silicon-carbon battery technology to increase battery capacity but does not greatly affect the overall design of the product. With large batteries, the device can provide long-term battery life to users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được trang bị viên pin lớn. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-pin.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-pin.jpg\" title=\"Xiaomi 15 Series được trang bị viên pin lớn. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xiaomi 15 Series is equipped with large batteries. Source: Gizmochina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Xiaomi 15 and Xiaomi 15 Pro duo also have improved camera systems to bring the best photography experience to users. This camera cluster is also fine-tuned and supported by Leica similar to the previous generation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How much does Xiaomi 15 Series cost?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The selling price of Xiaomi 15 Series in the Chinese market is as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xiaomi 15:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Optional 12 GB RAM, 256 GB internal memory costs 4,499 Yuan (about 15.9 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>Optional 12 GB RAM, 512 GB internal memory costs 4,799 Yuan (about 17 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>Optional 16 GB RAM, 512 GB internal memory costs 4,999 Yuan (about 17.7 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>Optional 16 GB RAM, 1 TB internal memory costs 5,499 Yuan (about 19.5 million VND).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xiaomi 15 Pro:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The 12 GB RAM, 256 GB internal memory version costs 5,299 Yuan (about 18.8 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>The 16 GB RAM version, 512 GB internal memory costs 5,799 Yuan (about 20.6 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>The 16 GB RAM version, 1 TB internal memory costs 6,499 Yuan (about 23 million VND).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Xiaomi 15 Series sở hữu mức giá tốt so với cấu hình. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-gia.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1571703/xiaomi-15-series-gia.jpg\" title=\"Xiaomi 15 Series sở hữu mức giá tốt so với cấu hình. Nguồn: Gizmochina.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xiaomi 15 Series has a good price compared to its configuration. Source: Gizmochina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Overall, these are good prices, which can be considered bargains compared to what the Xiaomi 15 Series is equipped with. So how do you rate the Xiaomi 15 Series? Please leave a comment below the article to let me know. Thank you for your interest and following.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'xiaomi-15-series-in-hand-luxurious-soft-design-powerful-configuration-with-snapdragon-8-elite', '2024-12-07 10:36:10', '2024-12-07 10:36:10', NULL),
(64, 2, 'OPPO Enco Air4 in hand: Compact design with good finishing quality, noise canceling support, strong battery life', '<h2>OPPO has introduced a new wireless headset model of the OPPO Enco line called <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/tai-nghe-bluetooth-true-wireless-oppo- enco-air-4-etee1\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OPPO Enco Air4\">OPPO Enco Air4</a>, a more affordable version of <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/tai-nghe-bluetooth-tws-oppo-enco-air-4-pro-etea1\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" OPPO Enco Air4 Pro\">OPPO Enco Air4 Pro</a> which the company introduced in May 2024. With me <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/tren-tay-oppo-enco-air4-1572421\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"on OPPO Enco hands Air4\">Hands on OPPO Enco Air4</a> see what&#39;s attractive about this wireless headset model.</h2>', '<h3><strong>Open the box and get your hands on OPPO Enco Air4 with beautiful appearance</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 is packaged in a square box with OPPO&#39;s signature white-gray color scheme. On the front of the box is printed the product name and an overview image of the product. Inside the OPPO Enco Air4 box contains accessories such as: User manual, 2 pairs of ear tips of different sizes next to the headset.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Hộp đựng OPPO Enco Air4 được thiết kế chỉn chu với kiểu dáng bắt mắt.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-01.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-01.jpg\" title=\"Hộp đựng OPPO Enco Air4 được thiết kế chỉn chu với kiểu dáng bắt mắt.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The OPPO Enco Air4 carrying case is carefully designed with an eye-catching design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Bên trong hộp đựng OPPO Enco Air4 chứa sách hướng dẫn sử dụng.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-02.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-02.jpg\" title=\"Bên trong hộp đựng OPPO Enco Air4 chứa sách hướng dẫn sử dụng.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inside the OPPO Enco Air4 box contains a user manual.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Hãng tặng thêm nhiều núm tai nghe để điều chỉnh kích thước tai.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-03.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-03.jpg\" title=\"Hãng tặng thêm nhiều núm tai nghe để điều chỉnh kích thước tai.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company offers many additional headphone tips to adjust ear size.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cuối cùng là mẫu tai nghe OPPO Enco Air4.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-04.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-04.jpg\" title=\"Cuối cùng là mẫu tai nghe OPPO Enco Air4.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, the OPPO Enco Air4 headphone model.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before getting to the headphones, I will first describe the OPPO Enco Air4 charging box. The OPPO Enco Air4 charging box is designed in a pebble shape with soft curved corners, edges, and front and back sides. With such a style and design, I can hold the charging box comfortably without straining my hands when using it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Hộp sạc OPPO Enco Air4 được thiết kế với kiểu dáng hình viên sỏi.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-08.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-08.jpg\" title=\"Hộp sạc OPPO Enco Air4 được thiết kế với kiểu dáng hình viên sỏi.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 charging box is designed with a pebble-shaped design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Phần cổng sạc được làm ở cạnh đáy.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-10.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-10.jpg\" title=\"Phần cổng sạc được làm ở cạnh đáy.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The charging port is made on the bottom edge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I consider the OPPO Enco Air4 charging box to be meticulously finished and sturdy even though the material is mainly plastic. However, because the surface of the charging box is glossy, the device easily attracts fingerprints when used.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Hộp sạc OPPO Enco Air4 có chất lượng hoàn thiện chỉn chu.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-09.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-09.jpg\" title=\"Hộp sạc OPPO Enco Air4 có chất lượng hoàn thiện chỉn chu.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 charging box has perfect quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Switching to the OPPO Enco Air4 headphones, this headphone model is designed with an in-ear design and a stubby, stubby stem. The feeling of wearing the OPPO Enco Air4 headset on the ear is very comfortable, fits well and does not feel like it easily falls off when you move.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tai nghe OPPO Enco Air4 được thiết kế kiểu dáng in-ear với chân stem ngắn.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-11.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-11.jpg\" title=\"Tai nghe OPPO Enco Air4 được thiết kế kiểu dáng in-ear với chân stem ngắn.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 headphones are designed in-ear style with short stem legs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>OPPO Enco Air4 offers good noise cancellation and good sound quality</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 uses Bluetooth 5.4 technology, so the device provides a seamless connection and sound experience. To use OPPO Enco Air4 well with mobile devices, people can download the HeyMelody application to adjust sound quality and features.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"OPPO Enco Air4 được hỗ trợ ứng dụng thứ 3 mang tên HeyMelody.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-18.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-18.jpg\" title=\"OPPO Enco Air4 được hỗ trợ ứng dụng thứ 3 mang tên HeyMelody.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 supports a third application called HeyMelody.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of sound experience, OPPO Enco Air4 provides a good sound experience, meeting the needs of using regular headphones. The plus point of the product for me is the device that supports active noise cancellation, thanks to which the product can limit noise when needing a quiet space to work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"OPPO Enco Air4 có chất âm ổn cùng khả năng chống ồn tốt.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-17.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-17.jpg\" title=\"OPPO Enco Air4 có chất âm ổn cùng khả năng chống ồn tốt.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 has stable sound quality and good noise canceling ability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, OPPO Enco Air4 also has another strong point in battery life with 11.5 hours of use and up to 42 hours when included with the charging box. Thanks to that, I don&#39;t have to worry about charging the battery when I use it for a few days.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How much does OPPO Enco Air4 cost?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently, OPPO Enco Air4 is on sale at Mobile World with a price of only 1,690 million VND with two colors for users to choose from: White, Green. This is a good price suitable for a device like OPPO Enco Air4.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"OPPO Enco Air4 sở hữu mức giá tốt phù hợp với những gì hãng trang bị trên sản phẩm.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-25.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572421/OPPO%20Enco%20Air%204-25.jpg\" title=\"OPPO Enco Air4 sở hữu mức giá tốt phù hợp với những gì hãng trang bị trên sản phẩm.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Enco Air4 has a good price suitable for what the company equips on the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So how do you rate OPPO Enco Air4? Please leave a comment below the article below, thank you for your interest and following.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'oppo-enco-air4-in-hand-compact-design-with-good-finishing-quality-noise-canceling-support-strong-battery-life', '2024-12-07 10:36:41', '2024-12-07 10:36:41', NULL),
(63, 2, 'HONOR Magic V3 in hand in Vietnam: Impressive slim design, Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 chip, 50 MP camera', '<h2>Among the foldable <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"phone\">phone</a> models that I have used Having had my hands on it so far, the HONOR Magic V3 is the product that impresses me the most in both its external design and internal configuration. I also had the opportunity to hold the HONOR Magic V3 in Vietnam and here are my initial feelings about this product.</h2>', '<h3><strong>HONOR Magic V3 in hand with slim, luxurious design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of appearance, HONOR Magic V3 is designed in a &quot;butterfly&quot; folding style similar to its predecessor - HONOR Magic V2 or many other folding smartphone models on the market. However, unlike many other brands, HONOR has optimized the entire product design to make the device light and compact so that users can have a better daily use experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3 được thiết kế theo dạng cánh bướm và sở hữu thân hình mỏng gọn.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-13.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-13.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3 được thiết kế theo dạng cánh bướm và sở hữu thân hình mỏng gọn.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is designed in the form of butterfly wings and has a slim body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exactly, the frame of the HONOR Magic V3 is only 9.2 mm thin when folded, and 4.35 mm when opened, the device height and width are 156.6 mm and 145.3 mm respectively. The size for me is to bring a neat, comfortable holding experience. Besides, the device also weighs only 226 grams, providing a comfortable grip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3 được thiết kế đẹp mắt cùng kích thước gọn gàng, cân nặng vừa phải.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-03.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-03.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3 được thiết kế đẹp mắt cùng kích thước gọn gàng, cân nặng vừa phải.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is beautifully designed with compact size and moderate weight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the frame of the HONOR Magic V3 is also designed in a curved shape, making the device very thin when looking at it. Even though it&#39;s thin, I feel like the finished device is very sturdy, so I&#39;m somewhat assured about the product&#39;s durability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Phần khung viền HONOR Magic V3 tuy mỏng nhưng lại được hoàn thiện rất cứng cáp.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-07.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-07.jpg\" title=\"Phần khung viền HONOR Magic V3 tuy mỏng nhưng lại được hoàn thiện rất cứng cáp.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The HONOR Magic V3 frame is thin but very sturdy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3&#39;s back is flat and slightly curved on all four edges. The back of the device is also made of smooth texture, so it effectively limits sweat and fingerprints. The camera cluster on the back is designed in a unique octagonal shape with a shiny metal frame surrounding it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mặt lưng hoàn thiện dạng nhám và được bo cong nhẹ.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-06.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-06.jpg\" title=\"Mặt lưng hoàn thiện dạng nhám và được bo cong nhẹ.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The back surface is finished in rough shape and is slightly curved on 4 edges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The front of HONOR Magic V3 is equipped with a 6.43 inch flat screen with a &quot;mole&quot; design. The device&#39;s secondary screen uses an OLED panel, FHD+ resolution and 120 Hz scan frequency. A good set of parameters, ensuring a sharp image display experience, bright colors and smooth image movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3 được trang bị màn hình phụ có chất lượng hiển thị tốt.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-14.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-14.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3 được trang bị màn hình phụ có chất lượng hiển thị tốt.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is equipped with a secondary screen with good display quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Switch to the HONOR Magic V3 main screen with a size of 7.92 inches, equipped with an LTPO AMOLED panel, 2K resolution and 120 Hz refresh rate. A set of parameters ensures that the user&#39;s vision will be &quot;satisfied&quot; with sharp images, vibrant colors and spacious display space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Màn hình trong cũng không ngoại lệ với màn hình lớn.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-24.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-24.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình trong cũng không ngoại lệ với màn hình lớn.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The internal screen is no exception to the large screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>HONOR Magic V3 powerful configuration with Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I will summarize all HONOR Magic V3 configuration parameters for everyone to follow the article.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Secondary screen: 6.43 inch size, OLED panel, FHD+ resolution, 120 Hz scan frequency.</li>\r\n	<li>Main screen: 7.92 inch size, LTPO AMOLED panel, 2K resolution, 120 Hz refresh rate.</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Snapdragon 8 Gen 3.</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 12 GB, 16 GB.</li>\r\n	<li>Internal memory: 256 GB, 512 GB or 1 TB</li>\r\n	<li>Rear camera: 50 MP + 50 MP + 40 MP.</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera: 20 MP (front and rear).</li>\r\n	<li>Battery capacity: 5,150 mAh, supports 66 W wired fast charging and 50 W wireless fast charging.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/tong-hop-chip-snapdragon-nam-2021-1339285\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Learn about Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor and many other powerful chips from Qualcomm\">Learn about Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor and many other powerful chips from Qualcomm</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Màn hình HONOR Magic V3 được trang bị bộ cấu hình xịn sò với chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 3.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-26.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-26.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình HONOR Magic V3 được trang bị bộ cấu hình xịn sò với chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 3.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 screen is equipped with a premium configuration with Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 chip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor. This processor is built on a 4 nm process with 8 cores clocked at 3.3 GHz. Comes with a new Adreno graphics core that helps provide up to 30% improved performance and 25% increased image processing capabilities compared to Snapdragon 8 Gen 2. Therefore, with Snapdragon 8 Gen3, HONOR Magic V3 can almost meet all your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3 với chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 có thể đáp ứng tốt nhu cầu sử dụng của người dùng cùng khả năng đa nhiệm mượt mà.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-30.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-30.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3 với chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 có thể đáp ứng tốt nhu cầu sử dụng của người dùng cùng khả năng đa nhiệm mượt mà.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 with Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 chip can well meet user needs with smooth multitasking capabilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, HONOR Magic V3 is equipped with a large battery (5,150 mAh) for a folding smartphone device. With this battery, the device can well meet the user&#39;s long-term use needs. In particular, the device is equipped with 66 W fast charging so users do not have to wait for the device to recover energy for too long.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>HONOR Magic V3 50 MP camera delivers impressive photos</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>I will summarize the HONOR Magic V3 camera parameters for everyone to follow the article.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Main camera: Resolution 50 MP f/1.6, PDAF, OIS.</li>\r\n	<li>Telephoto camera: 50 MP f/3.0 resolution, PDAF, OIS, 3X Zoom.</li>\r\n	<li>Ultra wide-angle camera: 40 MP f/2.2 resolution, AF.</li>\r\n	<li>Selfie camera: 20 MP resolution (Front and rear).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3 được trang bị bộ camera xịn sò với độ phân giải 50 MP.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-37.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-37.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3 được trang bị bộ camera xịn sò với độ phân giải 50 MP.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is equipped with a superb camera set with 50 MP resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this set of camera parameters, HONOR Magic V3 can make you satisfied with the photography experience with clear photos, realistic colors, and high contrast in many different lighting conditions. You can look at a few photos below to better understand the device&#39;s photography capabilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ HONOR Magic V3.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/IMG_20241201_141757.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/IMG_20241201_141757.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ HONOR Magic V3.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photo taken from HONOR Magic V3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ HONOR Magic V3.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/IMG_20241201_141634.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/IMG_20241201_141634.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ HONOR Magic V3.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photo taken from HONOR Magic V3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ HONOR Magic V3.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/IMG_20241201_141453.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/IMG_20241201_141453.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ HONOR Magic V3.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photo taken from HONOR Magic V3.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Summary</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Summing up, HONOR Magic V3 is an impressive product from HONOR in terms of slim appearance, device durability as well as powerful configuration with Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 chip and quality camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3 là mẫu smartphone gập tốt và đáng trải nghiệm.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-43.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572808/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-43.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3 là mẫu smartphone gập tốt và đáng trải nghiệm.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is a good folding smartphone model and worth experiencing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So how do you rate the HONOR Magic V3? Please leave a comment below the article to let me know. Thank you for your interest and following.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'honor-magic-v3-in-hand-in-vietnam-impressive-slim-design-snapdragon-8-gen-3-chip-50-mp-camera', '2024-12-07 10:37:01', '2024-12-07 10:37:01', NULL),
(62, 2, 'HONOR Magic V3: The pinnacle of folding phones, durability, impact resistance and more', '<h2>The folding <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"smartphone\">smartphone</a> market is increasingly vibrant with the participation of many technology giants. Among them, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/honor-magic-v3\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3\">HONOR Magic V3<!-- a--> emerges as a bright candidate with outstanding improvements in design, durability, performance and user experience. Let&#39;s explore whether the HONOR Magic V3 is the pinnacle of the current folding phone!</a></h2>', '<h3><strong>Ultra-thin design with outstanding durability</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-07.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-07.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 makes a strong impression with its ultra-thin design, only 9.2 mm when folded and 4.35 mm when opened, weighing only 226 grams. This is the thinnest folding phone in the world today, providing a comfortable grip, easy to pocket and carry with you. This design is achieved thanks to a combination of many factors, including the use of lightweight materials, optimization of the internal structure and a new hinge design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only thin and light, HONOR Magic V3 is also made from super durable materials, including special carbon fiber for the aerospace industry, helping to enhance impact resistance up to 40 times compared to other Ordinary materials. This type of carbon fiber is often used in aircraft and spacecraft manufacturing, providing outstanding durability for HONOR Magic V3.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Folding screen without creases, seamless experience</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-25.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-25.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A big plus point for the HONOR Magic V3 is that the folding screen has no crease in the middle. Thanks to the advanced &quot;Floating waterdrop hinge&quot; hinge technology, the screen folds smoothly, creating a seamless flat surface that does not obstruct when watching movies, playing games or working. This hinge is designed to distribute force evenly when folded, minimizing pressure on the screen and preventing creases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.92 inch LTPO AMOLED main screen with 2K resolution, 120 Hz refresh rate for sharp, vivid and smooth display quality. The 6.43-inch OLED secondary screen also possesses impressive parameters, with high brightness up to 2,500 nits, ensuring a great experience even when you do not turn on the device.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Powerful performance, super large battery</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-35.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-35.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is equipped with a powerful Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor, combined with 12 GB LPDDR5X RAM and up to 1 TB UFS 4.0 internal memory, providing outstanding performance, smooth processing of every task. tasks, from basic applications to graphics-intensive games. With this configuration, HONOR Magic V3 can &quot;weigh&quot; all of today&#39;s hottest mobile games without any problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large capacity 5,150 mAh battery allows comfortable use all day long, even when you use it at high intensity. 66W wired fast charging technology helps you fully charge the battery in a short time, only about 40 minutes, ready for all activities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Top notch camera, capturing every moment</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"vHONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-04.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-04.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 possesses an impressive camera system with a 50 MP main camera, a 50 MP telephoto camera that supports 3.5x optical zoom and a 40 MP ultra wide-angle camera. The main camera is equipped with a Sony IMX858 sensor with f/1.6 aperture, supports OIS optical image stabilization, allowing for sharp photos in low light conditions. The telephoto camera is also equipped with OIS, helping you zoom far while maintaining stability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Both selfie cameras have 20 MP for sharp, natural photo quality. Smart AI features support professional photography and 4K video recording, helping you preserve every memorable moment with excellent quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Other highlights on HONOR Magic V3</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-15.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-15.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the above outstanding advantages, HONOR Magic V3 also scores points with many other attractive features such as: MagicOS 8.0.1 operating system based on Android 14 with a friendly interface and many personalization options. This interface is designed specifically for folding phones, optimizing the user experience on large screens.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High quality stereo speakers, fine-tuned by IMAX Enhanced, provide a vivid, realistic sound experience when watching movies and listening to music. IPX8 water resistance, protects the device safely when exposed to water. You can safely use your phone in the rain or accidentally drop it into water.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Conclusion</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-555.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572911/HONOR%20Magic%20V3-555.jpg\" title=\"HONOR Magic V3: Đỉnh cao điện thoại gập, bền bỉ, chống va đập và hơn thế nữa\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HONOR Magic V3 is a comprehensive folding phone, converging the most advanced technology today. With a thin and light design, outstanding durability, fold-free screen, powerful performance, top-notch camera and many smart features, HONOR Magic V3 deserves to be the top choice for those who are looking for a classy and different folding smartphone.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'honor-magic-v3-the-pinnacle-of-folding-phones-durability-impact-resistance-and-more', '2024-12-07 10:37:36', '2024-12-07 10:37:36', NULL),
(61, 2, 'Overview of the Vivo V40 5G launch and experience event in Vietnam: Convergence of essence', '<h2>Recently, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-vivo\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"vivo\">vivo</a> Vietnam has officially Model launch formula <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"smartphone\">smartphone</a> completely new mine - <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/vivo-v40-5g\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"vivo V40 5G\">vivo V40 5G</a>. Along with that, the vivo V40 5G experience event also had the presence of a series of KOLs and famous stars.</h2>', '<h3><strong>Overview of vivo V40 5G experience event</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It is known that the vivo V40 5G experience event was held at ROS Yacht Club located at Ben Bach Dang, 10B Ton Duc Thang, Ben Nghe Ward, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City. The event starts at 7:00 p.m. on December 6.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Sự kiện trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G được tổ chức tại ROS Yacht Club \" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%207.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%207.jpg\" title=\"Sự kiện trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G được tổ chức tại ROS Yacht Club \" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>vivo V40 5G experience event held at ROS Yacht Club</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When participating in the event, customers also have the opportunity to receive many attractive gifts when checking in, including: A special corner card of today&#39;s most popular stars, along with teddy bears from vivo and a series of other attractive gifts are waiting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tại sự kiện có rất nhiều quà tặng thú vị đang chờ đợi\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%203.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%203.jpg\" title=\"Tại sự kiện có rất nhiều quà tặng thú vị đang chờ đợi\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the event, there are many interesting gifts waiting</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here, customers attending the event can also experience many new features with vivo V40 5G. Along with that, the ability to take photos from the Zeiss camera on vivo V40 5G combined with the dynamic evening atmosphere in Saigon promises to bring unprecedented experiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Rất nhiều khách mời tham gia trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%202.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%202.jpg\" title=\"Rất nhiều khách mời tham gia trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many guests participated in the vivo V40 5G experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Along with that, customers participating in the event also have the opportunity to meet and interact with leading experts in many different fields, such as: Photography, creativity, fashion and entertainment, . etc. Furthermore, at the event there was also the appearance of &quot;beautiful sister&quot; DJ Mie and model Mai Ngo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Sự kiện trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G còn có sự góp mặt của người mẫu Mai Ngô và DJ Mie\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%204.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%204.jpg\" title=\"Sự kiện trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G còn có sự góp mặt của người mẫu Mai Ngô và DJ Mie\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The vivo V40 5G experience event also had the participation of model Mai Ngo and DJ Mie</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vivo V40 5G promises to stir up the market in the near future, with a design full of dynamic and personality. Along with a powerful configuration combined with a sharp Zeiss camera system. V40 5G promises to bring unparalleled experiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Sự kiện trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G hứa hẹn sẽ đem tới những sự thú vị chưa từng có\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%209.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%209.jpg\" title=\"Sự kiện trải nghiệm vivo V40 5G hứa hẹn sẽ đem tới những sự thú vị chưa từng có\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The vivo V40 5G experience event promises to bring unprecedented excitement</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>vivo V40 5G configuration parameters</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>vivo V40 5G is the company&#39;s latest smartphone model that inherits a completely new design language. The device&#39;s middle frame is made of high-quality plastic and the back is made of glass. vivo V40 5G has an extremely compact and easy-to-hold design with a thickness of only 7.58 mm and a weight of 190 grams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"vivo V40 5G có thiết kế mỏng nhẹ và cực kỳ gọn gàng trong lòng bàn tay\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%208.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%208.jpg\" title=\"vivo V40 5G có thiết kế mỏng nhẹ và cực kỳ gọn gàng trong lòng bàn tay\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>vivo V40 5G has a thin, light and extremely compact design in the palm of your hand</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The display capabilities of vivo V40 5G are extremely impressive, the device is equipped with a 6.78-inch edge-to-edge curved AMOLED screen, 1.5K resolution and 120 Hz refresh rate. Along with that, the panel on V40 5G also supports maximum brightness of 4,500 nits, color coverage of 100% DCI-P3 and pixel density of 405 PPI.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"vivo V40 5G được trang bị màn hình cong tràn cạnh đẹp mắt\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%2010.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%2010.jpg\" title=\"vivo V40 5G được trang bị màn hình cong tràn cạnh đẹp mắt\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>vivo V40 5G is equipped with a beautiful curved edge-to-edge screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Powering the vivo V40 5G is the Snapdragon 7 Gen 3 processor, combined with 12 GB of LPDDR4X RAM that can be expanded by 12 GB and 256 GB of UFS 2.2 internal memory. vivo V40 5G is equipped with a BlueVolt battery with a capacity of 5,500 mAh, supporting 80 W wired fast charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Toàn bộ thông số cấu hình của vivo V40 5G\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/Logo%2024h%20c%C3%B4ng%20ngh%E1%BB%87.psd.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/Logo%2024h%20c%C3%B4ng%20ngh%E1%BB%87.psd.jpeg\" title=\"Toàn bộ thông số cấu hình của vivo V40 5G\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All configuration parameters of vivo V40 5G</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vivo V40 5G is also equipped with a 50 MP wide-angle main camera and a 50 MP ultra-wide-angle camera, both with lenses tuned by Zeiss. Meanwhile, the front of vivo V40 5G is equipped with a 50 MP selfie camera also tweaked by Zeiss. Furthermore, V40 5G also brings vivo&#39;s signature signature with Aura LED flash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Đèn LED Aura đặt trưng trên vivo V40 5G\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%2011.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572909/V40%205G%2011.jpg\" title=\"Đèn LED Aura đặt trưng trên vivo V40 5G\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aura LED lights featured on vivo V40 5G</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, vivo V40 5G also supports many other wireless connection standards, including: Wi-Fi 5, Bluetooth 5.4, NFC, OTG, 5G network connection support and USB Type-C charging port. Regarding software, vivo V40 5G runs on the Funtouch OS 14 interface based on the Android 14 platform. The device is also IP68 water and dust resistant | IP69.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'overview-of-the-vivo-v40-5g-launch-and-experience-event-in-vietnam-convergence-of-essence', '2024-12-07 10:38:03', '2024-12-07 10:38:03', NULL),
(60, 2, 'Galaxy M16 appeared on Geekbench with Dimensity 6300 chip', '<h2><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/samsung\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Samsung\">Samsung</a> seems to be preparing to launch the Galaxy M16 5G, model <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"phone\">phone</a> new cheap belongs to the M-series line. This smartphone has just appeared on Geekbench, considered the successor to <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-m15\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Galaxy M15 5G\">Galaxy M15 5G</a> launches in April 2024.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy M16 5G with model number SM-M166P achieved 552 single-core points and 1611 multi-core points in the Geekbench test. These scores surpass the Galaxy A16 (even though both use the same Dimensity 6300 chip), which reached 514 and 1464 points, showing the possibility that the device has improvements in the cooling system or software optimization to prioritize performance.</p>', '<p>Based on Samsung&#39;s tradition of keeping similarities between the M series and A series, the Galaxy M16 5G may share many hardware with <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/ samsung-galaxy-a16-5g\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Galaxy A16 5G\">Galaxy A16 5G</a>. Expected specifications include a 6.7-inch Full HD+ Super AMOLED screen with a 90 Hz refresh rate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The device is expected to have a 3-rear camera system including: 50 MP main sensor, 5 MP super wide-angle lens and 2 MP macro camera, and 13 MP front camera. The device may be equipped with a 5000 mAh battery that supports 25 W fast charging, similar to its predecessor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"camera\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572650/A%CC%89nh%20ma%CC%80n%20hi%CC%80nh%202024-11-29%20lu%CC%81c%2016.39.11.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572650/A%CC%89nh%20ma%CC%80n%20hi%CC%80nh%202024-11-29%20lu%CC%81c%2016.39.11.jpeg\" title=\"camera\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy M16 5G is expected to have camera parameters similar to Galaxy A16 5G (Photo: Samsung)</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'galaxy-m16-appeared-on-geekbench-with-dimensity-6300-chip', '2024-12-07 10:38:24', '2024-12-07 10:38:24', NULL);
