(59, 2, '3 super simple ways to fix iOS 18 battery drain error that 90% of iPhone users don\'t know about', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">iOS 18, the latest operating system version from Apple, brings many attractive features and outstanding improvements. However, many users have complained about rapid battery drain after updating to iOS 18. If you are also experiencing this &quot;headache&quot; problem, don&#39;t worry! This article will provide you with <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/cach-other-phuc-loi-ios-18-hao-pin-1568144\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"how to fix iOS 18 battery drain error\">how to fix iOS 18 battery drain error</a>, helping you fully enjoy the wonderful experiences on your device <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"phone\">phone</a> my iPhone.</span></strong></p>', '<h2>iOS 18, the latest operating system version from Apple, brings many attractive features and outstanding improvements. However, many users have complained about rapid battery drain after updating to iOS 18. If you are also experiencing this &quot;headache&quot; problem, don&#39;t worry! This article will provide you with <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/cach-other-phuc-loi-ios-18-hao-pin-1568144\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"how to fix iOS 18 battery drain error\">how to fix iOS 18 battery drain error</a>, helping you fully enjoy the wonderful experiences on your device <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"phone\">phone</a> my iPhone.</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>1. Turn on battery saving mode</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Turning on battery saving mode on iOS 18 is a quick and effective solution to reduce battery drain. When enabled, this mode automatically adjusts background activities, screen brightness, refresh rate, and several other features to save power. Although it may reduce device performance slightly, battery saving mode will significantly extend battery life, especially useful in necessary situations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"cách khắc phục lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/0/iphone-15-pro-lifestyle-10-1280x720.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/0/iphone-15-pro-lifestyle-10-1280x720.jpg\" title=\"cách khắc phục lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Consider turning on this mode as a temporary &quot;lifesaver&quot; to maintain your iPhone&#39;s operation when the battery is low, and learn the causes and other solutions to completely fix the battery drain problem. on iOS 18. Go to <strong>Settings</strong> &gt; Select <strong>Battery</strong> &gt; Proceed to <strong>Turn on low power mode</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/10-1280x1280.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/10-1280x1280.jpg\" title=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. Turn off background app refresh</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Turning off background app refresh is one of the effective ways to minimize battery drain on iOS 18. When this feature is enabled, apps will continuously update new data even when you don&#39;t use them. This means they still operate in the background and consume significant battery power. By turning off background app refresh, you can prevent this automatic update process, helping to save battery life and extend the life of your device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"cách khắc phục lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/0/iphone-15-pro-lifestyle-21(1)-1280x720.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/0/iphone-15-pro-lifestyle-21(1)-1280x720.jpg\" title=\"cách khắc phục lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To turn off background app refresh, follow these steps:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Go to <strong>Settings </strong>&gt; Select <strong>General Settings</strong> &gt; Click to select <strong>Background App Refresh. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/12-1280x1280.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/12-1280x1280.jpg\" title=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Select next <strong>Refresh apps in the background</strong>&gt; Here you choose <strong>Turn off</strong> so the system can save more battery for you. my device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/11-1280x1280.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/11-1280x1280.jpg\" title=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Use auto brightness</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Automatic brightness is a useful feature that significantly saves battery life on iOS 18. When enabled, iPhone will automatically adjust screen brightness based on ambient light conditions. This means the screen will not be too bright when not needed, thereby reducing power consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, not having to constantly adjust the brightness manually also helps reduce operations and saves time for users. So, turn on the automatic brightness feature to extend the battery life on your iPhone!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Open <strong>Settings </strong>on your phone &gt; Swipe down and select <strong>Accessibility &gt; </strong>Tap next to select <strong>Screen &amp; Font Size </strong>&gt; Scroll to the bottom and<strong> Turn on Auto-Brightness.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/13-1280x1280.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/News/1567427/13-1280x1280.jpg\" title=\"cách sửa lỗi iOS 18 hao pin\" /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '3-super-simple-ways-to-fix-ios-18-battery-drain-error-that-90-of-iphone-users-dont-know-about', '2024-12-07 10:38:44', '2024-12-07 10:38:44', NULL),
(58, 2, 'ASUS ROG Phone 9 Series launched: Snapdragon 8 Elite chip, aggressive design and a series of top gaming accessories', '<h2>Recently, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-asus\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"ASUS\">ASUS</a> officially presented Brand new gaming phone line - ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ASUS ROG Phone 9 Pro. Accordingly, this <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"smartphone\">smartphone</a> line possesses a very unique design. Extremely rugged, with powerful configuration with Snapdragon 8 Elite processor.</h2>', '<h3><strong>Configuration parameters of ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ASUS ROG Phone 9 Pro</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>First of all, in terms of appearance, ASUS ROG Phone 9 and 9 Pro have a completely flat front, along with soft curved edges for a more comfortable gaming experience. The back of the device is finished with nano-texture material to help prevent fingerprints better. Both models meet IP68 water and dust resistance standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mặt lưng của ROG Phone 9 Series có khả năng chống bám dấu vân tay cực tốt\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%202.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%202.jpg\" title=\"Mặt lưng của ROG Phone 9 Series có khả năng chống bám dấu vân tay cực tốt\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The back of ROG Phone 9 Series is extremely resistant to fingerprints</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Along with that, the back of ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ROG Phone 9 Pro also integrates the Anime Vision feature with more than 648 mini-LED bulbs. Furthermore, ASUS this time also developed a new application called Anime Play that can turn the Anime Vision screen into a classic game console through ROG AirTrigger.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Màn hình Anime Vision và tính năng Anime Play mới trên ROG Phone 9 và ROG Phone 9 Pro\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%201.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%201.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình Anime Vision và tính năng Anime Play mới trên ROG Phone 9 và ROG Phone 9 Pro\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>New Anime Vision screen and Anime Play feature on ROG Phone 9 and ROG Phone 9 Pro</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next, ROG Phone 9 and ROG Phone 9 Pro are supported with a series of new AI features to make the gaming experience more interesting. With X Sense, this feature will help gamers automatically pick up items, automatically record highlight moments in the game and along with a series of other smart AI features.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tính năng X Sense sẽ là một trở thủ đắc lực dành riêng cho game thủ\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%203.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%203.jpg\" title=\"Tính năng X Sense sẽ là một trở thủ đắc lực dành riêng cho game thủ\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The X Sense feature will be an effective assistant for gamers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next is the display ability, ROG Phone 9 Series is equipped with an AMOLED E6 screen, 6.78 inches in size, variable scan frequency of 1-120 Hz and the highest scan frequency up to 185 Hz when playing games. . The panel on the ROG Phone 9 Series also produces a maximum brightness of 2,500 nits and supports HDR10. The screen is also covered with Gorilla Glass Victus 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Màn hình trên ROG Phone 9 Series có tần số quét lên đến 185 Hz\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%2010.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%2010.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình trên ROG Phone 9 Series có tần số quét lên đến 185 Hz\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The screen on ROG Phone 9 Series has a scan frequency of up to 185 Hz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of performance, ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ROG Phone 9 Pro are equipped with Snapdragon 8 Elite processor, combined with up to 24 GB of LPDDR5X RAM and up to 1 TB of standard internal memory. UFS 4.0. Along with that, ASUS also supports the exclusive X Mode feature on ROG Phone 9 Series to help increase gaming performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ROG Phone 9 Series được trang bị vi xử lý Snapdragon 8 Elite mạnh mẽ\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%204.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%204.jpg\" title=\"ROG Phone 9 Series được trang bị vi xử lý Snapdragon 8 Elite mạnh mẽ\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ROG Phone 9 Series is equipped with a powerful Snapdragon 8 Elite processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of heat dissipation performance, ASUS has developed Gamecool 9 cooling technology with the ability to dissipate heat up to 360 degrees around the device. With a 5-zone cooling structure, along with a 57% wider graphite heatsink layer, it increases heat dissipation efficiency by up to 17%. Furthermore, ROG Phone 9 Series also supports the Aeroactive Cooler X Pro cooling fan combined with a control button on the body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Công nghệ tản nhiệt Gamecool 9 trên ASUS ROG Phone 9 Series\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%205-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%205-1.jpg\" title=\"Công nghệ tản nhiệt Gamecool 9 trên ASUS ROG Phone 9 Series\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gamecool 9 heat dissipation technology on ASUS ROG Phone 9 Series</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the Aeroactive Cooler X Pro cooling fan with integrated physical gaming buttons, ASUS also offers a completely new ROG Tessen controller. This controller supports a series of different shortcut keys, along with users can easily customize the buttons according to their own optimal operation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tay cầm chơi game ROG Tessen hoàn toàn mới\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%206.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%206.jpg\" title=\"Tay cầm chơi game ROG Tessen hoàn toàn mới\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All-new ROG Tessen game controller</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of camera, ROG Phone 9 Series is equipped with a 50 MP Sony LYT-700 main camera, supports 2X lossless zoom along with 6-axis Hybrid Gimbal Stabilizer 4.0 anti-shake capability. Along with that, both devices are combined with a 13 MP super wide-angle camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Thông số camera trên ROG Phone 9 Series\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%207.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%207.jpg\" title=\"Thông số camera trên ROG Phone 9 Series\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera specifications on ROG Phone 9 Series</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, the difference on ROG Phone 9 Pro is that the 32 MP telephoto camera supports 3X optical zoom, but on the ROG Phone 9 it is equipped with a 5 MP tele macro camera. On the front, both models are equipped with a 32 MP selfie camera. Furthermore, the AirTrigger button now also supports the ability to focus and take photos quickly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Điểm khác biệt giữa của hệ thống camera trên ROG Phone 9 và ROG Phone 9 Pro\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%208.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%208.jpg\" title=\"Điểm khác biệt giữa của hệ thống camera trên ROG Phone 9 và ROG Phone 9 Pro\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The difference between the camera system on ROG Phone 9 and ROG Phone 9 Pro</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not stopping there, ROG Phone 9 Series now also supports a series of new AI features, such as: Circle to search, call translation, speech to text, AI wallpaper. Powering the ROG Phone 9 Series is a 5,800 mAh battery, supporting 65 W fast wired charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ROG Phone 9 Series được trang bị viên pin 5.800 mAh\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%2011.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%2011.jpg\" title=\"ROG Phone 9 Series được trang bị viên pin 5.800 mAh\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ROG Phone 9 Series is equipped with a 5,800 mAh battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Toàn bộ thông số kỹ thuật của ASUS ROG Phone 9 và ROG Phone 9 Pro\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%2012.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572306/ROG%20Phone%209%20-%2012.jpg\" title=\"Toàn bộ thông số kỹ thuật của ASUS ROG Phone 9 và ROG Phone 9 Pro\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full specifications of ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ROG Phone 9 Pro</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Price of ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ASUS ROG Phone 9 Pro</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>ASUS ROG Phone 9 offers users two different color options, including: Storm White and Phantom Black. Meanwhile, the ROG Phone 9 Pro offers users a Phantom Black color option. In foreign markets, ASUS ROG Phone 9 and ASUS ROG Phone 9 Pro have the following prices and configuration options:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ASUS ROG Phone 9 has a starting price of 1,099 EUR (about 29.4 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>ASUS ROG Phone 9 Pro has a starting price of 1,299 EUR (about 34.8 million VND).</li>\r\n	<li>ASUS ROG Phone 9 Pro Edition has a starting price of 1,499 EUR (about 40.2 million VND).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>What do you think about ASUS ROG Phone 9 Series?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'asus-rog-phone-9-series-launched-snapdragon-8-elite-chip-aggressive-design-and-a-series-of-top-gaming-accessories', '2024-12-07 10:39:32', '2024-12-07 10:39:32', NULL),
(57, 2, 'Genuine OPPO Find X8 Pro in hand: The most impressive flagship model from OPPO', '<h2>After a long wait, I finally got it <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/tren-tay-oppo-find-x8-pro-chinh-hang- 1572618\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"genuine OPPO Find X8 Pro in hand\">genuine OPPO Find X8 Pro in hand</a>. This is the latest <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"smartphone\">smartphone</a> model of the OPPO Find X series as of now current time. Let&#39;s find out <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/oppo-find-x8-pro\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OPPO Find X8 Pro\">OPPO Find X8 Pro</a> check out the article below!</h2>', '<h3><strong>Hands on OPPO Find X8 Pro with premium design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of appearance, OPPO Find X8 Pro is designed with a 2.5D curved screen on all 4 sides and measures 6.78 inches (the back is also similarly designed). The frame of the device is designed to be square with corners and slightly curved edges to provide a comfortable holding experience for the user.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"OPPO Find X8 Pro được thiết kế theo kiểu dáng vuông vức với mặt tước bo cong 2.5D.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-1.jpg\" title=\"OPPO Find X8 Pro được thiết kế theo kiểu dáng vuông vức với mặt tước bo cong 2.5D.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Find X8 Pro is designed in a square design with a 2.5D curved surface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talking a little about the OPPO Find X8 Pro screen, the device screen is equipped with an LTPO AMOLED panel, 1.5K+ resolution, 120 Hz refresh rate and maximum screen brightness of 4,500 nits. A good set of parameters ensures the device can display clear and sharp images to the user.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Màn hình OPPO Find X8 Pro cho trải nghiệm hiển thị tuyệt vời.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-2.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình OPPO Find X8 Pro cho trải nghiệm hiển thị tuyệt vời.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Find X8 Pro screen provides a great display experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The frame of the OPPO Find A special feature is that OPPO is equipped with a Burst Shot photography button on the right side of the device with the function of quickly activating the camera and taking photos, adjusting the zoom level. You can take a look at the border in the photos below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Đính máy OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa mic phụ.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-3.jpg\" title=\"Đính máy OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa mic phụ.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The OPPO Find X8 Pro device contains a secondary microphone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cạnh phải của OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa cần gạt âm thanh với ba mức là Bình thường, Rung và Im lặng.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-4.jpg\" title=\"Cạnh phải của OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa cần gạt âm thanh với ba mức là Bình thường, Rung và Im lặng.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The right edge of OPPO Find X8 Pro contains a sound lever with three levels: Normal, Vibrate and Silent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cạnh phải của OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa nút nguồn, cụm phím tăng giảm âm lượng cùng nút chụp ảnh Burst Shot.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-5.jpg\" title=\"Cạnh phải của OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa nút nguồn, cụm phím tăng giảm âm lượng cùng nút chụp ảnh Burst Shot.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The right edge of OPPO Find X8 Pro contains the power button, volume up and down keys and Burst Shot photography button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cạnh đáy OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa mic, khe cắm SIM, dải loa và cổng sạc USB-C.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-6.jpg\" title=\"Cạnh đáy OPPO Find X8 Pro chứa mic, khe cắm SIM, dải loa và cổng sạc USB-C.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The bottom edge of OPPO Find X8 Pro contains a mic, SIM slot, speaker strip and USB-C charging port.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Switching to the back of OPPO Find In Vietnam, OPPO Find X8 Pro has two versions for you to choose when buying: White and Black, the version I am using is black.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Mặt lưng OPPO Find X8 Pro được hoàn thiện từ kính nhám với cụm camera lớn.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-7.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-7.jpg\" title=\"Mặt lưng OPPO Find X8 Pro được hoàn thiện từ kính nhám với cụm camera lớn.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The back of OPPO Find X8 Pro is finished from matte glass with a large camera cluster.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The back of OPPO Find X8 Pro also stands out with a large circular camera cluster located in the middle of the back. Surrounding the camera cluster is a meticulously designed jagged border showing the manufacturer&#39;s meticulousness, and inside the camera frame there are 4 lenses arranged in a cross shape with the Hasselblad logo in the center.<!-- p--></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>OPPO Find X8 Pro has powerful configuration with Dimensity 9400 chip</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Below is a summary table of OPPO Find X8 Pro configuration parameters, specifically as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen: 6.78 inches, AMOLED, 2,760 x 1,256 pixels, 120 Hz refresh rate, maximum screen brightness 4,500 nits.</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: MediaTek Dimensity 9400.</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 16 GB.</li>\r\n	<li>Internal memory:512 GB.</li>\r\n	<li>Rear camera: 50 MP (main camera) + 50 MP (ultra wide-angle camera) + 50 MP (Hasselblad telephoto camera) + 50 MP (telephoto camera).</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera: 32 MP.</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 5,910 mAh, 80 W wired fast charging, 50 W wireless fast charging.</li>\r\n	<li>Operating system: ColorOS 15 - Android 15.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/mediatek-dimensity-9400-ra-mat-hieu-suat-cuc-cao-nang-tam-trai-nghiem -ai-1570900\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MediaTek Dimensity 9400 launched: Extremely high performance, enhanced experience AI experience\">MediaTek Dimensity 9400 launched: Extreme performance, enhancing AI experience</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"OPPO Find X8 Pro được trang bị chip xử lý MediaTek Dimensity 9400.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-8.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-8.jpg\" title=\"OPPO Find X8 Pro được trang bị chip xử lý MediaTek Dimensity 9400.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Find X8 Pro is equipped with MediaTek Dimensity 9400 processor chip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you can see above, OPPO Find predecessor. It can be said that the device can bring great performance to meet all user needs. I will have a more detailed review for everyone to refer to.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Với chip Dimensity 9400 thì OPPO Find X8 Pro có thể đáp ứng tốt nhu cầu sử dụng của người dùng.\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-9.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572618/tgdd-oppo-find-x8-pro-9.jpg\" title=\"Với chip Dimensity 9400 thì OPPO Find X8 Pro có thể đáp ứng tốt nhu cầu sử dụng của người dùng.\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Dimensity 9400 chip, OPPO Find X8 Pro can meet the user&#39;s needs well.</p>\r\n\