(56, 2, 'Galaxy Z Flip7 and Galaxy Z Fold7 will have the upgrades you\'ve always wanted', '<h2><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/samsung\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Samsung\">Samsung</a> remains the largest folding phone brand Currently, however, this position is gradually shaking. Chinese rivals are launching foldable phones with better specs, thinner and lighter, and lower prices. However, perhaps with the Galaxy Z Flip7 and Galaxy Z Fold7 there will be a larger screen - the upgrade you&#39;ve always wanted!</h2>', '<h1>Galaxy Z Flip7 and Galaxy Z Fold7 will have the upgrades you&#39;ve always wanted</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Galaxy Z Flip7 và Galaxy Z Fold7 sẽ có màn hình lớn hơn\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572742/galaxy-w25-1T.jpg\" title=\"Galaxy Z Flip7 và Galaxy Z Fold7 sẽ có màn hình lớn hơn\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/samsung\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Samsung\">Samsung</a> remains the largest folding phone brand Currently, however, this position is gradually shaking. Chinese rivals are launching foldable phones with better specs, thinner and lighter, and lower prices. However, perhaps with the Galaxy Z Flip7 and Galaxy Z Fold7 there will be a larger screen - the upgrade you&#39;ve always wanted!</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Galaxy Z Flip7 and Galaxy Z Fold7 will have larger screens</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>According to sources from Ross Young, Galaxy Z Flip7 and Galaxy Z Fold7 will have larger screens. Specifically, the Galaxy Z Fold7 is said to have a 6.5-inch external screen and an 8-inch internal screen, similar to the Galaxy Z Fold SE or Samsung W25. The Galaxy Z Flip 7 is said to have a 6.85-inch internal screen and a 4-inch secondary screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Galaxy Z Flip7 và Galaxy Z Fold7 sẽ có màn hình lớn hơn\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572742/nda-samsung-galaxy-zfold-6-22.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-s