atic/common/News/1572348/tgdd-galaxy-a06-20.jpg\" title=\"Galaxy A06 đạt doanh số ấn tượng ngay trong thời gian đầu\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This configuration is enough to meet basic usage needs such as surfing the web, watching movies, and playing light games. In particular, the large capacity battery of 5,000 mAh allows comfortable use of up to 2 days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Galaxy A06 đạt doanh số ấn tượng ngay trong thời gian đầu\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572348/tgdd-galaxy-a06-10.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572348/tgdd-galaxy-a06-10.jpg\" title=\"Galaxy A06 đạt doanh số ấn tượng ngay trong thời gian đầu\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only that, the Galaxy A06 is also equipped with a 50 MP main camera and a 2 MP secondary camera, allowing users to take photos with high detail and good color reproduction. Along with that is a sharp 8 MP selfie camera, good enough for basic photography needs and video calling via chat or online meeting applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Samsung brand - Solid launcher</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Galaxy A06 đạt doanh số ấn tượng ngay trong thời gian đầu\" data-original=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572348/tgdd-galaxy-a06-31.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/News/1572348/tgdd-galaxy-a06-31.jpg\" title=\"Galaxy A06 đạt doanh số ấn tượng ngay trong thời gian đầu\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung has long been an electronic brand trusted and chosen by Vietnamese users. With a reputation that has been affirmed over many years, Samsung always provides users with quality products, high durability and good after-sales service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the One UI Core 5.0 interface based on the Android 13 operating system pre-installed on the Galaxy A06 provides a smooth, easy-to-use user experience. Another valuable plus point of the Galaxy A06 is Samsung&#39;s commitment to long-term software update support. This ensures users always experie