&acirc;y, gi&uacute;p bạn dễ d&agrave;ng nạp pin m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cần th&aacute;o t&uacute;i đựng ra.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'tui-dung-airpods-pro-2-nhua-pc-tpu-uniq-clyde-lock-case', '2024-11-24 06:53:28', '2024-11-24 06:53:28', NULL),
