(67, 2, 'iPhone 16 Pro Max phone', NULL, '<aside id=\"slider-detail\">\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-1-638639778344066754.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Tổng Quan\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-1-638639778344066754.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-1-638639778344066754.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Tổng Quan\" /></a><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-2-638639778356775849.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Thông Số Kỹ Thuật\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-2-638639778356775849.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-2-638639778356775849.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Thông Số Kỹ Thuật\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>With the explosive launch of version <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone-16-series\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone series 16 at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16</a>, Apple has continued to affirm its position in the smartphone market with revolutionary innovations. Possessing exquisite design, advanced technology and outstanding performance has made <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-pro\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\" _blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Pro at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Pro</a> becomes one of the most notable technology products of the year, giving users a futuristic experience within reach.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Promotional program when purchasing iPhone 16 Series during the on-sale period (applicable until October 31, 2024)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Buy accessories for up to 15% discount.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Discount on Apple products purchased together, especially up to 500k off when purchased with an iPad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Renewable old collection program: Additional discount of up to 2,000,000 VND (applies depending on the old device model, does not include payment via gateway incentives).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Easy payment: 0% installment payment with credit card, no down payment required. Browse profiles in just 3 minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 16 series is an upgraded board with many valuable improvements compared to the iPhone 15 series. With a powerful A18 chip, graphics performance and energy saving capabilities are significantly improved compared to the A16 chip on iPhone. 15.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 48 MP &quot;Fusion&quot; camera is a highlight that provides the ability to take sharp photos in low light conditions. At the same time, spatial video recording and 3D macro photography turn moments into vivid photos and videos. In addition, the Camera Control button provides quick operation, super sensitive touch and is easily compatible with third-party applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Dynamic Island display from the iPhone 15 remains the same for the iPhone 16 Series, along with improvements to True Tone, P3 wide color, and Haptic Touch. However, the 120Hz refresh rate added in the Pro and Pro Max versions is the highlight, providing a smoother experience for users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 16 Plus and Pro Max are even superior with longer battery life combined with MagSafe fast charging up to 25W. This is a huge step forward in performance and user experience, well worth upgrading from iPhone 15.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Overview of iPhone 16 Pro</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 16 Pro and iPhone 16 Pro Max are the two most advanced versions in the iPhone 16 line, introduced by Apple with sophisticated design, advanced technology and outstanding performance. The Pro version has an ultra-light titanium frame, providing high durability with four diverse color options: Natural Titanium, White Titanium, Black Titanium and Desert Titanium.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Action Button - multi-functional action button, allowing users to highly customize and experience new interactions. 6.3-inch Super Retina XDR OLED screen, with a maximum brightness of 2000 nits, uses ProMotion 120Hz technology and A18 Pro chip to provide powerful performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3-lens camera system, including 48MP main camera, 48M super wide-angle cameraP and 12MP telephoto camera, supporting 5x optical zoom, for outstanding photo and video quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery life is improved, allowing users to use comfortably for 27 hours continuously. In addition, compared to the iPhone 16 Pro Max series, the iPhone 16 Pro has an additional 128GB memory option suitable for customers who do not need to store too much information.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Improved luxury and ultimate durability</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 16 Pro 128GB enhances the sophistication of its design with an ultra-light titanium frame, providing both durability and an elegant feel every time you hold it. The lightness and hardness of titanium material helps reduce the weight of the machine without losing the necessary sturdiness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/f5/17/f5178d2f227b467f9fa7ffc26988e105.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Tổng quan (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/f5/17/f5178d2f227b467f9fa7ffc26988e105.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/f5/17/f5178d2f227b467f9fa7ffc26988e105.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Tổng quan (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With soft rounded edges, this 16 Pro version provides a comfortable grip, even when used for long periods of time. The colors of the device also carry a modern impression with many typical color versions, creating luxury and sparkle when light shines on them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The design of the phone does not stop at external beauty but also optimizes the user experience. With the addition of a multi-function task button and Camera Control button located on the long side of the device, Apple has brought convenience and faster access to users. This is a big step forward compared to previous generations, helping to enhance the user experience and beauty of the device.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Action Button new experience, easier to use</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most outstanding features of this launch is the Action Button (multi-function task button), a highly customizable key, supporting users to install and use in different ways. its own. From quickly switching between sound modes, activating your favorite features, to launching apps with just a tap, Action Button opens up a new era in how to interact with smartphones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This feature not only makes using iPhone more convenient but also enhances personalization. Users can easily adjust and customize this key according to their habits and needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The ultimate visual experience through eye-catching frames</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more phone models at Thegioididong.com\">Phone<!-- a--> equipped </a><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/man-hinh-super-retina-xdr-tren-iphone-11-pro-va-11-1198630\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Find understand Super Retina XDR display technology on iPhone\">6.3 inch Super Retina when used outdoors. This is one of the company&#39;s brightest screens, allowing users to clearly see displayed content even under strong sunlight.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/75/af/75af79e10ca16309fc48103a7b6dd3b4.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Màn hình (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/75/af/75af79e10ca16309fc48103a7b6dd3b4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/75/af/75af79e10ca16309fc48103a7b6dd3b4.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Màn hình (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ProMotion technology with an adaptive refresh rate of up to 120 Hz is one of the most notable upgrades of this version, providing a smooth experience when surfing the web, playing games or watching videos. The combination of high brightness, fast refresh rate and HDR technology has created a screen that is not only beautiful but also extremely responsive, bringing the ultimate visual experience to users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>True Tone technology helps the screen of iPhone 16 Pro 128GB adjust color and brightness automatically based on ambient light. Protects users&#39; eyes but also provides more accurate and natural colors when viewing content.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Professional mobile photography</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera system of <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to other iPhone models at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone&lt; /a&gt; has also been significantly improved, giving users superior photo and video capabilities. Cluster of 3 rear cameras with high resolution, including 48 MP main camera, </a><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/camera-goc-rong-goc-sieu-rong-tren- smartphone-la-1172240\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"What is a wide-angle camera? How to take photos with a super wide-angle camera\">ultra wide-angle camera</a> 48 MP and <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/camera-tele-la-gi-danh-gia-uu-nhuoc-diem-1542185\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Camera Tele What is it? Evaluate the pros and cons of the Tele Camera\">telephoto camera</a> 12 MP with the ability to <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/optical-zoom-on-camera-smartphone-la-gi-1172374\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"What is optical zoom? Yes What stands out? Which phone has optical zoom?\">optical zoom</a> up to 5x, allowing users to take detailed and vivid photos in all lighting conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Camera Control button is also a big highlight of this iPhone 16 Pro 128GB. Now, you only need a light touch to take a photo, instead of having to move your finger down the screen like before. This feature not only simplifies the photography process but also helps you capture beautiful moments quickly and accurately, especially useful when you want to capture unexpected moments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/39/39/39392d13ca0abddacf2eeb16c56748b5.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Camera (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/39/39/39392d13ca0abddacf2eeb16c56748b5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/39/39/39392d13ca0abddacf2eeb16c56748b5.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Camera (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides, the device also supports 4K video recording <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/dolby-vision-la-gi-cac-ung-dung-noi- bat-and-but-loai-1226284\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"What is Dolby Vision? What are the highlights? Which devices have Dolby Vision?\">Dolby Vision</a>&#39;s speed is 120 fps, delivering excellent image quality with high detail and vivid colors. This is a very important feature for those working in the field of content production or simply want to preserve memorable moments with the highest quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Convert the colors of photos more professionally with just a few simple steps thanks to the Photography Style technology built into the device. Helps you freely transform each photo in your own style, from classic to modern colors, from vivid to quiet. Every photo is now a work of art bearing your own personal impression.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>High performance from the new chip generation, solving all requirements</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Inside <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-choi-game\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more models of high-configuration gaming phones other at Thegioididong.com\">this high-configuration gaming phone</a> is the Apple A18 Pro chip, built on a 3nm process, providing superior performance and more energy saving than previous generations. system before. The A18 Pro chip is not only faster but also smarter, helping to handle every task smoothly, from heavy AAA games to recording and editing videos in 4K resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/da/18/da182a32d3a0c82c8aaabad8ccc943b3.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Hiệu năng (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/da/18/da182a32d3a0c82c8aaabad8ccc943b3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/common/Products/42/329143/da/18/da182a32d3a0c82c8aaabad8ccc943b3.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - Hiệu năng (Nguồn: Apple.com)\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The processing power of this new chip is clearly demonstrated through 6 CPU cores, providing impressive processing power, allowing the device to operate smoothly even when running resource-demanding applications. High. Comes with a 6-core GPU with improved architecture, creating a big step forward in graphics capabilities. When compared to the previous generation, this new device can process graphics up to 30% faster than <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone-15-series\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more iPhone 15 series at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 15</a> and double that of iPhone 12.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the new 16-core Neural Engine, the device&#39;s artificial intelligence becomes smarter and more responsive. Finding information, editing text or asking questions is now easier and faster, making interactions between users and devices more natural and smooth, just like a conversation. conversation between two people, opening up many new potential applications in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-3-638639778380823123.jpg\" onclick=\"return false; \"><img alt=\"iPhone 16 Pro - AI và Pin\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-3-638639778380823123.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/42/329143/iphone-16-pro-3-638639778380823123.jpg\" title=\"iPhone 16 Pro - AI và Pin\" /></a></p>\r\n</aside>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iphone-16-pro-max-phone', '2024-12-09 17:27:36', '2024-12-09 17:27:36', NULL),
(68, 2, 'iPhone 15 Pro Max phone', NULL, '<h3>In the increasingly developing world of technology, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-15-pro-max-1tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"References iPhone 15 Pro Max 1TB at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 15 Pro Max 1TB</a> stands out as a perfect smartphone, combining the power of technology and unlimited creativity. This phone not only offers outstanding performance but also offers excellent photography capabilities, creating a perfect experience for users.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Luxury, sturdy appearance</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB still maintains the square and classy design that has made this product line famous. Maintaining the traditional appearance not only shows luxury and elegance but also helps users immediately recognize that this is an iPhone.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs an important change, the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB has abandoned the familiar stainless steel frame material to switch to using a Titanium frame. This not only makes the phone more sturdy, but also helps reduce overall weight, providing more comfort when used for long periods of time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-102854.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-102854.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-102854.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The back of the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is made from high-quality tempered glass and crafted in a rough style, creating a unique beauty and highlighting the overall design. At the same time, this material also makes the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the phone at Thegioididong.com\">phone</a> becomes more scratch-resistant and reduces fingerprints.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dynamic Island is a unique feature on the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB. This is a feature that works on the pill-shaped notch of the screen, allowing users to quickly access applications and functions through animated icons. This helps optimize user convenience and increase productivity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103025.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103025.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103025.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Use Type-C port instead of Lightning</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most important changes in the design of the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is the switch from the familiar Lightning port to the standard Type-C port. This decision marks Apple&#39;s progress and innovation in providing users with a more modern and flexible connectivity experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/usb-type-c-chuan-muc-cong-ket-noi-moi-723760\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"What is USB Type C? What are the advantages and disadvantages compared to traditional USB?\">What is USB Type C? What are the advantages and disadvantages compared to traditional USB?</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Type-C port on iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB, users can quickly share data, charge the battery and connect to accessories they can use every day without having to search conversion cable.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Equiped with three top-notch rear cameras</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the camera, the phone integrates 3 cameras including: 48 MP main camera, 12 MP telephoto camera and 12 MP super wide-angle camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 48 MP resolution, the smallest details are reproduced delicately and the ability to take photos in low light conditions is noteworthy. Whether you&#39;re capturing beautiful nature or sharing family moments, the main camera always delivers sharp and vivid photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is not only a great tool for photography but also for recording high-quality videos. With the ability to record 4K video at a frame rate of 60 fps, you will have smooth and sharp videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103905.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103905.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103905.jpg\" title=\"Camera điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are a lover of sports and outdoor activities, the 2.8K Action Mode video recording feature will be the perfect choice. This is a powerful tool for you to record your adventurous and unique activities with stable and sharp images.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another choice for you is the product <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-pro-max-1tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference Check out iPhone 16 Pro Max 1TB at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Pro Max 1TB</a> will make you fall in love with its versatile camera system. With high resolution, fast autofocus and many professional photography features, you can create ultimate artistic photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103910.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103910.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-103910.jpg\" title=\"Camera điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Using a high-frequency OLED screen</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With OLED technology, the screen on the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB provides colors with peak contrast and brightness. This makes every color appear vivid and realistic. You can see each color with its own sophistication and style.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OLED technology works by self-emitting light from each pixel on the screen. This means that each pixel has the ability to adjust its own brightness without the need for a backlight. The result is extremely accurate color reproduction and the screen can turn off individual pixels to produce high contrast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/man-hinh-oled-la-gi-905762\" target=\"_blank\">What is OLED screen? What stands out? Which devices have OLED screens?</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104241.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104241.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104241.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The iPhone 15&#39;s screen has a resolution of 1290 x 2796 pixels, meaning every pixel on the screen is very small and almost impossible to see with the naked eye. Each of these tiny pixels work together to reproduce every detail and line with absolute precision. This creates images that are sharp and deep, allowing you to see every single feature in every image.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a large size of up to 6.7 inches, the screen of iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB provides a spacious and comfortable space to view content. This makes browsing the web, watching videos, and even playing games on your phone especially enjoyable. You can be fully immersed in the content you love, and the large screen helps you enjoy every detail optimally.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB display supports a refresh rate of up to 120 Hz, providing an amazingly smooth experience for scrolling, playing games, and watching videos. This smooth, fast display makes every interaction on the screen more enjoyable and pleasing to the eye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The brightness of the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB screen is also impressive, with the ability to reach 2000 nits. This allows you to use the phone easily even in strong sunlight and the content on the screen is always clear and easy to read.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Supports fast charging</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is equipped with a large capacity battery, helping you use the phone comfortably all day long. Whether you&#39;re browsing the web, watching videos, or using heavy apps, this iPhone&#39;s battery ensures you&#39;re not interrupted by constant recharging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To ensure you don&#39;t spend too much time recharging the battery, the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB supports 20 W fast charging technology. This means you can charge from 0% up to full power. in a short time, helping you save time and always be ready for every task.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104602.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Pin và sạc điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104602.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104602.jpg\" title=\"Pin và sạc điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only does it have a large battery capacity and fast charging, the iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is also equipped with smart power management through iOS 17. This helps optimize battery performance, ensuring that Energy is used effectively without waste. You can use your phone smartly without worrying about the battery running out soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Performance that breaks all limits</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Apple always holds the right to control and develop its own processor chip and the Apple A17 Pro is no exception. With powerful performance, this processor helps iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB run smoothly, reliably and quickly. You can perform many difficult tasks without any problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/chip-a17-bionic-tien-trinh-3nm-tien-tien-1522727\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Apple A17 Pro Chip - Advanced 3nm process, extremely powerful performance\">Apple A17 Pro Chip - Advanced 3nm process, extremely powerful performance</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 8 GB of RAM, the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-choi-game\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to high-configuration gaming phones at The Gioi This Mobile\">high-spec gaming phone</a> will never experience interruptions or lag. This is especially useful when you&#39;re playing games, editing videos, or dealing with resource-intensive applications. You can easily switch between apps without any glitches.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104358.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Cấu hình điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104358.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/299033/iphone-15-pro-130923-104358.jpg\" title=\"Cấu hình điện thoại - iPhone 15 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The iOS 17 operating system brings many significant improvements in features and performance. It optimizes the interaction between hardware and software, helping the phone operate smoothly and save battery life. New and improved features in iOS 17 help you work, play, and browse the web quickly and conveniently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/toan-bo-thong-tin-ve-ios-17-ngay-ra-mat-tinh-nang-1525071 \">Official iOS 17: When is it released, what&#39;s new, which devices does it support?</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Should I buy iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is a high-end smartphone with many outstanding advantages, including beautiful design, powerful performance, great camera and reasonable price. If you are looking for a phone that can meet all your needs, the iPhone 15 Pro Max is a choice worth considering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And to experience the full sound on iPhone 15 Pro Max, don&#39;t forget to connect to <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-mxp63\" target=\" _blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 headphones at Thegioididong.com\">AirPods 4</a> for ultimate sound quality or <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-chong-on-mxp93\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 ANC at Thegioididong.com\">AirPods 4 ANC&lt; /a&gt; to immerse yourself in a separate world, undisturbed by surrounding noise.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-chong-on-mxp93\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 ANC at Thegioididong.com\">Reasons for choosing to buy iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB at Mobile World</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-chong-on-mxp93\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 ANC at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB is the most anticipated high-end smartphone of 2023. With many new and improved features, iPhone 15 Pro Max 1 TB will definitely be a great choice for users who are looking for a phone with strong performance, quality cameras and luxurious design.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-chong-on-mxp93\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 ANC at Thegioididong.com\"><strong>&bull; Genuine products, quality assurance:</strong>Mobile World is the largest mobile phone retailer in Vietnam, committed to providing genuine products, quality assurance quantity. You can rest assured about the product&#39;s origin and can enjoy the best using experience.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-chong-on-mxp93\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 ANC at Thegioididong.com\"><strong>&bull; Attractive offers and promotions:</strong> Mobile World regularly has promotions, discounts and fr