(69, 2, 'iPhone 14 Pro Max phone', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-14-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 14 Pro Max at Mobile World\">iPhone 14 Pro Max</a> a masterpiece in the smartphone world was launched by Apple in September 2022. The device is equipped with an extremely powerful Apple A16 Bionic chip, accompanied by a new screen design, promising to bring new experiences to iPhone users.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>High-end durable design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This year&#39;s iPhone will inherit features from its older brother <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-13-pro-max-1tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 13 Pro Max at Mobile World\">iPhone 13 Pro Max</a>, will still have a stainless steel frame and tempered glass back combined with a modern square shape through shaping. flat on the edges and back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103221.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế sang trọng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103221.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103221.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế sang trọng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This year&#39;s Pro line was launched with many color options and the most prominent of them is probably the Deep Purple (purple) version, because this is a new color so it brings quite high recognition.&lt; /p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103227.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màu sắc mới mẻ - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103227.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103227.jpg\" title=\"Màu sắc mới mẻ - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, Apple has just launched the product line <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone-16-series\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 series at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16</a>, with the perfect combination of performance, design and price, bringing a great product experience for you. With different versions that promise to meet all your needs: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 regular</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-plus\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Plus at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Plus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-pro\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Pro at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Pro Max at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Pro Max</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Stand out with new screen design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The most impressive point on <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more genuine iPhones being sold at Mobile World \">iPhone</a> this year lies in the screen design, it can be easily seen that the company has also removed the traditional rabbit ears over many iPhone generations with an extremely strange new shape. p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế hình notch mới - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế hình notch mới - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compared to this year&#39;s notch-shaped rabbit ears, there is a relatively good space saving, but compared to other &quot;mole&quot; screen types, this is still not really an optimal thing for the screen. screen. But Apple knows how to take advantage of disadvantages to turn them into spectacular advantages by inventing many interesting effects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Kích thước nhỏ gọn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" title=\"Kích thước nhỏ gọn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To make them more eye-catching Apple has also introduced many motion effects to increase user enjoyment, this is activated while I hold down the notch image while using the parts. Support software such as: Listening to music, timer, recording,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiệu ứng sinh động - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" title=\"Hiệu ứng sinh động - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Display more realistic content through a quality display</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to now, OLED panels have always been highly appreciated by the user community when appearing on Apple product lines, with the iPhone 14 Pro Max this is no exception when the image that the device bring utmost authenticity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình cao cấp - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình cao cấp - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking at the screen, we will see a clarity that is extremely pleasing to the eye, the content displayed has depth, the feeling when watching movies or playing games also becomes more vivid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most outstanding point that this panel brings is the color accuracy. I also used the iPhone 14 Pro Max to design a few publications such as simple posters or stickers and the results were printed later. when comparing with the photo above <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more Genuine, cheap phones doing business at Mobile World\">phone</a> is almost are equal, the deviation is not too significant, which helps me feel more secure in designing images.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Độ chuẩn xác về màu cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\" title=\"Độ chuẩn xác về màu cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The screen resolution reaches 2796 x 1290 Pixels, so reproducing highly detailed images is very easy. Phenomena like screen pitting are something I have never seen appear on a phone. for 2 weeks of experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103242.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Độ chi tiết cực lớn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103242.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103242.jpg\" title=\"Độ chi tiết cực lớn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Supports Always On Display feature</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the notch innovation, this year Apple also equipped the Pro and Pro Max lines with Always On Display technology, which allows the device to not turn off the screen completely but still display the screen. Locked with a fairly low brightness, enough for me to quickly read notifications to see the date and time quite conveniently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/always-on-display-la-gi-co-hao-pin-khong-huong-dan-1169208\" target=\"_blank\">What is Always On Display? Does it waste battery? How to turn it on and off</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103239.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"TÍnh năng trên màn hình - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103239.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103239.jpg\" title=\"TÍnh năng trên màn hình - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, the screen is quite dark at this time, so using it outdoors will be a bit difficult to see. Besides, this feature will also reduce battery life more than usual. Leaving the phone overnight for about 7 hours in Always On Display mode will lose about 3 - 4% of the battery capacity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Scan frequency 120 Hz</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 14 Pro Max has a very high scanning frequency, so all my daily operations are responded quickly, the feeling of touching and swiping has also become more enjoyable, the phenomenon of pauses or delays while swiping has been reduced. Significant improvement compared to 60 Hz screen standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Vuốt chạm mượt mà - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\" title=\"Vuốt chạm mượt mà - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, Apple also added an option to help you easily adjust the scanning frequency to 120 Hz or down to 60 Hz depending on your needs, suitable for use in emergency situations such as want to save battery to ensure the device can maintain long-term use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Brightness 2000 nits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compared to other competitors in the segment, a brightness of 2000 nits is considered an outstanding advantage that few brands can match, so is it helpful and is it really effective? must be something many people wonder about.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Độ sáng màn hình cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" title=\"Độ sáng màn hình cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifically, the high-brightness screen has helped me a lot in all my daily needs, since using the iPhone 14 Pro Max to view maps while on the street during bad weather. The harsh sunlight also becomes easier, the screen is not too dark or glare, and the directions are also clearly displayed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Độ sáng màn hình cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" title=\"Độ sáng màn hình cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, when taking photos outdoors in the sun, high screen brightness will also be an advantage. It is useful when adjusting the shooting angle when all grid lines are clearly displayed and the subject is clearly visible. whether or not I have focus, I can easily observe directly on the screen without having to use my hands to block the light like most other phones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ceramic Shield tempered glass</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ceramic Shield is probably no longer a strange term for most users as this is considered a type of technology that has appeared in the iPhone 12 generation, this standard is famous for its extremely high durability and Very good resistance to scratches.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In fact, I tested the durability of this glass surface by scratching other easily accessible objects such as: Keychains, charging cords, ballpoint pens and even glasses frames. The results I received were also very impressive, the screen was almost undamaged without any scratches appearing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103250.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Mặt kính kháng xước - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103250.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103250.jpg\" title=\"Mặt kính kháng xước - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, this is also a test so the force used to scratch is not too great, so users should not be too subjective about dropping situations. This just helps me feel more secure in placing the phone face down on a flat surface or placing it with other objects without worrying about scratches.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Capture every moment through the 48 MP main camera</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Normal mode photo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before going into the experience evaluation section, let&#39;s briefly review the camera parameters of the iPhone 14 Pro Max, this year&#39;s device will still be arranged with a cluster of 3 cameras, of which the main sensor has a resolution of 48 MP, 12 MP wide-angle sensor and finally a 12 MP telephoto lens. With such impressive parameters, the device promises to become <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-chup-anh-camy-phim\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Electronic Reference Mobile World photo and video phones\">top photo and video phones</a> in 2022.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photos taken under normal conditions produce results that I am very satisfied with. Images are reproduced with high detail, colors are displayed very realistically, images when zoomed in will not be too broken, helping the composition to work. Zooming in or changing the frame does not change the quality too much.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103252.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103252.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103252.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103256.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103256.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103256.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most satisfactory point about the camera is its ability to balance extremely well, the image quality produced has a neutral color gamut, without the phenomenon of yellow or green cast like on some smartphones of other brands. other competitors in the market. This makes editing photos easier because I no longer need to adjust the hue to bring them back to their original color.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103259.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103259.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103259.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ultra wide-angle photo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the super wide-angle shooting mode through the 12 MP secondary sensor, I am very satisfied with the results, the photos are still highly detailed, every scene in front of me is almost fully captured. Inside the photo, the extended areas are not distorted or reduce image quality, making the overall image very high quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103301.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103301.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103301.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103303.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103303.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103303.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Backlit photo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Darkness or glare is considered a common situation for regular smartphones, but on the iPhone 14 Pro Max, this has been significantly improved through the Smart HDR 4 feature.&lt; /p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103306.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103306.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103306.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When facing sources with high brightness, the phone will automatically identify the subject and scene, thereby brightening the areas that need to be focused and reducing the brightness of the remaining positions to help My photos become easier to see, in addition, it also helps my photos become more artistic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Telephoto photo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In telephoto shooting mode, the phone supports us with many levels of adjustment from 2X, 3X to 5X and 10X,... However, the device will only support maximum optical zoom up to 3X and With larger levels, the phone will switch to digital zoom mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photos taken from optical zoom mode will use a separate camera with 12 MP resolution to focus. The resulting image quality will still be highly detailed, everything will be preserved almost intact. version and not much different from the photos taken from the default mode, but to avoid misunderstandings, this is just a comparison example if you don&#39;t look too closely at the resolution ratio of both. .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103308.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103308.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103308.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103310.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103310.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103310.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the photos taken with the digital zoom feature, the photos I took are still quite good. Here, the phone&#39;s camera will work with the same principle as if you were cropping your photo with a frame. The image and scale are smaller, so the image quality will be somewhat poorer than the default capture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103312.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103312.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103312.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>But thanks to the main camera&#39;s high resolution and high level of detail, when taking photos using digital zoom mode, the photos still have good detail, all objects and scenes are captured. relatively clear.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Photo of a colorful scene</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This year, Apple has communicated quite a lot about the additional features and types of technology on the camera of the iPhone 14 Pro Max. The most mentioned names are probably Deep Fusion, Smart HDR 4 and Dolby Vision. HDR.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103314.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103314.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103314.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>These are considered technologies that are almost never present on any Android phone, so this is the outstanding advantage that I highly appreciate on the iPhone 14 Pro Max&#39;s camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In fact, the phone&#39;s photos have very similar colors to real life, extremely high detail, areas with separate colors do not appear to blend together, the overall picture is The photo makes me feel very good-looking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103316.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103316.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103316.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103318.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103318.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103318.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Because it supports the Deep Fusion feature, the device is capable of taking a total of 9 photos while taking a photo, from which the device will automatically analyze to produce a photo with good detail. as best quality for display. So, even though my hands were shaking slightly during the shoot, the resulting photo was not blurry or out of focus.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iphone-14-pro-max-phone', '2024-12-09 17:28:41', '2024-12-09 17:28:41', NULL),
(70, 2, 'iPhone 13 Pro Max phone', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-13-pro-max\">iPhone 13 Pro Max 128 GB</a> - the most anticipated super product in the late 2021 comes from <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/apple\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the main iPhone smartphone prices company\">Apple</a>. The device&#39;s design is not very groundbreaking compared to its predecessor. Inside, this is still a product with a super beautiful screen, the scanning frequency has been upgraded to a smooth 120 Hz, the camera sensor is larger in size, with strong performance and the power from Apple A15 Bionic, ready to conquer all challenges with you.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Top class design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.topzone.vn/iphone-13\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 13 sales at TopZone\">iPhone 13</a> inherits the design Featured from the iPhone 12 Pro Max with a square frame, glass back and an edge-to-edge rabbit-ear screen at the front.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-3.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế vuông vức đặc trưng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-3.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế vuông vức đặc trưng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With <a href=\"https://www.topzone.vn/iphone/iphone-13-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 13 Pro Max for sale at TopZone\">iPhone 13 Pro Max</a>&#39;s rabbit ears have been shrunk by 20% compared to the previous generation, not only freeing up more display space but also helping the front of the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business phones at Mobile World\">phone</a> becomes more attractive while still ensuring ensure the operation of the sensors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình tai thỏ được tinh giản - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-2.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình tai thỏ được tinh giản - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The easily recognizable change on the iPhone 13 Pro Max is that the size of the rear camera sensor is larger and to increase recognition of the new product, Apple has also added a Sierra color option. Blue (lighter blue than the Pacific Blue of the iPhone 12 Pro Max).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-9.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Sierra Blue trẻ trung, thanh lịch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-9.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-9.jpg\" title=\"Sierra Blue trẻ trung, thanh lịch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The machine continues to use a high-quality steel frame for outstanding scratch and impact resistance, combined with IP68 dust and water resistance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more:<a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/tieu-chuan-chong-nuoc-ip68-tren-smartphone-la-gi-co-cong-1396848\" target=\"_blank\">What is the IP68 waterproof standard on smartphones? What is the use?</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-4.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Viền thép cao cấp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-4.jpg\" title=\"Viền thép cao cấp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Super smooth entertainment screen with 120 Hz refresh rate</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 13 Pro Max is equipped with a 6.7-inch screen with a resolution of 1284 x 2778 Pixels, using an OLED panel and Super Retina XDR technology for outstanding energy saving while still ensuring a clear display. sharp, vivid and realistic visuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-5.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình kích thước 6.7 inch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-5.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình kích thước 6.7 inch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This year&#39;s iPhone Pro Max has been upgraded to a 120 Hz refresh rate, all transitions when gliding fingers on the screen become smoother and visual effects when we play games or watch videos also extremely satisfying.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apple has just launched the product line <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone-16-series\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 series at Thegioididong .com\">iPhone 16</a>, with the perfect combination of performance, design and price, brings you a great product experience. With different versions that promise to meet all your needs: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 regular</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-plus\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Plus at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Plus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-pro\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Pro at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-16-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 16 Pro Max at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 16 Pro Max</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-6.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tốc độ làm tươi màn hình - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-6.jpg\" title=\"Tốc độ làm tươi màn hình - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With smart ProMotion technology, it can change the scanning frequency from 10 to 120 times per second depending on the application and operation you are using, to optimize battery life and your experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Công nghệ ProMotion thông minh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-1.jpg\" title=\"Công nghệ ProMotion thông minh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you use iPhone 13 Pro Max to play games, the 120 Hz refresh rate combined with the GPU&#39;s excellent graphics performance will make the device extremely perfect to experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-8.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Mang đến trải nghiệm mượt mà - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-8.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-8.jpg\" title=\"Mang đến trải nghiệm mượt mà - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the device also supports True Tone technology, a wide P3 cinematic color range that will make all your experiences on the device more impressive than ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-20.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Dải màu chuẩn điện ảnh P3 - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-20.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-20.jpg\" title=\"Dải màu chuẩn điện ảnh P3 - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Comprehensive upgraded camera cluster</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 13 Pro Max will still have a set of 3-lens cameras arranged alternately in a square cluster, located in the upper left corner of the back of the device including a telephoto camera, super wide-angle camera and wide-angle main camera with f/ aperture. 1.5 super large.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-21.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Cụm camera chuyên nghiệp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-21.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-21.jpg\" title=\"Cụm camera chuyên nghiệp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The super wide-angle camera has also been upgraded with f/1.8 aperture, faster sensor, providing natural and realistic super wide-angle photos and also enhanced with the ability to focus at a distance of only 2 cm, providing exciting macro photography and video recording features.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-10.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Lấy nét ở khoảng cách 2cm - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-10.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-10.jpg\" title=\"Lấy nét ở khoảng cách 2cm - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The telephoto camera on iPhone 13 Pro Max can optically zoom 3x, enlarging images and videos 3 times while maintaining the same quality, supporting portrait photography <a href=\"https://www. thegioididong.com/dtdd-camera-xoa-phong\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the price of smartphone cameras for taking pictures with blurred background\">clear background</a>, with many built-in natural color filters help get The photo is exactly as expected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-11.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Khả năng zoom quang học - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-11.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-11.jpg\" title=\"Khả năng zoom quang học - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the LiDAR sensor will still be present on iPhone 13 Pro Max to provide the best augmented reality (AR) experience for all users as well as support for camera clusters focusing in the environment. low light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-12.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Lấy nét trong môi trường anh sáng yếu - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-12.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-12.jpg\" title=\"Lấy nét trong môi trường anh sáng yếu - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apple also enhances photography capabilities on iPhone 13 Pro Max with a Cinematic standard movie recording mode that helps users easily focus on subjects both during and after recording, while blurring the background and other characters in the frame.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-13.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chế độ quay Cinematic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-13.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-13.jpg\" title=\"Chế độ quay Cinematic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s also the first smartphone to offer a professional &quot;end-to-end&quot; workflow that lets you record and edit videos in ProRes or Dolby Vision compression with a variety of advanced settings creating significantly shortens the post-production process to create amazing quality movies right on your phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-14.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Khả năng quay video chuyên nghiệp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-14.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-14.jpg\" title=\"Khả năng quay video chuyên nghiệp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>See now the hottest new iPhone launches of 2023 - <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-15-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tam Check out iPhone 15 Pro Max at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 15 Pro Max</a> with full information about specifications, colors and capacity versions. In addition, quickly leave your information at Mobile World for a chance to receive it soon <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone-15-series\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 15 series at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 15</a> on September 29.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Promising performance with Apple A15 Bionic</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 13 Pro Max will be equipped with the company&#39;s latest Apple A15 Bionic processor, manufactured on a 5 nm process, ensuring impressive operating performance while still saving the best power. Ability to support super high-speed 5G network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to Apple&#39;s announcement, A15 Bionic is the fastest chipset in the smartphone world (September 2021), with 50% faster speed than other chips on the market, able to perform 15.8 trillion calculations per seconds, making CPU performance faster than ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-15.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Vi xử lý Apple A15 Bionic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-15.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-15.jpg\" title=\"Vi xử lý Apple A15 Bionic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The device has 128 GB of internal memory, just enough for the needs of a basic user who does not need to record too much video. In addition, this year there is also an internal memory version of up to 1TB. , you can consider if you have high storage needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-16.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Dung lượng bộ nhớ - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-16.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-16.jpg\" title=\"Dung lượng bộ nhớ - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the device also integrates Wi-Fi 6 technology, a new wireless connection standard equipped with multiple 5G bands, compatible with many carriers in different countries, iPhone 13 Pro Max always provides maximum network speed, for a smooth experience of watching 4K movies, downloading files in the blink of an eye, and playing online games without delay anywhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-17.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Kết nối nhanh chóng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-17.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-17.jpg\" title=\"Kết nối nhanh chóng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A leap in battery life</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone Pro Max marks a new turning point in battery life. With a large battery capacity combined with a new screen and power-saving Apple A15 Bionic processor, making iPhone 13 Pro Max the iPhone with the best battery life ever, 2.5 hours longer than with predecessor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-18.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chip A15 giúp tối ưu hóa năng lượng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-18.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-18.jpg\" title=\"Chip A15 giúp tối ưu hóa năng lượng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unfortunately, the battery capacity of the new iPhone models has improved, but their fast charging speed is still only at 20 W via wired connection and charging via MagSafe at a maximum of 15 W or can be via Qi-based wireless charger with 7.5 W power.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-19.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Sạc MagSafe - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-19.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-19.jpg\" title=\"Sạc MagSafe - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apple has constantly improved to bring users the best products, iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB still retains the highlights of its predecessor, featuring improvements in configuration, battery life as well as camera and many things waiting for you to discover.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iphone-13-pro-max-phone', '2024-12-09 17:28:55', '2024-12-09 17:28:55', NULL);
