information at Mobile World to receive <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone-15-series\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 15 series at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 15</a> earliest on September 29.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-2-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Sự thay đổi về thiết kế vượt trội | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-2-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-2-1.jpg\" title=\"Sự thay đổi về thiết kế vượt trội | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the iPad Pro 2020 uses monolithic aluminum material, then <a href=\"https://www.topzone.vn/iphone-12\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the iPhone 12 product line at TopZone, Mobile World\'s brand\">iPhone 12</a> Pro Max will be made of glass and steel frame, making users more reminded of the legendary iPhone 4/4s duo with beautiful design. The best in Apple&#39;s design history.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-4-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Mặt lưng bằng kính, khung viền thép được thiết kế cho máy | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-4-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-4-1.jpg\" title=\"Mặt lưng bằng kính, khung viền thép được thiết kế cho máy | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The difference with the 4/4s duo lies in the fact that the glass surface of the iPhone 12 Pro Max is slightly curved, helping to fit the frame perfectly, creating a seamless screen when held and in use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.topzone.vn/iphone/iphone-12-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone 12 Pro Max at TopZone\">iPhone 12 Pro Max</a> will have an impressive thickness of only 7.4 mm, which is about 10% thinner than <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-11-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the price of genuine iPhone 11 Pro Max at Thegioididong.com\" type=\" Check the price of genuine iPhone 11 Pro Max at Thegioididong.com\">iPhone 11 Pro Max</a> is currently 8.1 mm. This further increases the charm and class of the device from every angle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-6-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế bắt mắt từ mọi góc nhìn | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-6-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-6-1.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế bắt mắt từ mọi góc nhìn | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Excellent display quality</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 12 Pro Max is equipped with a 6.7-inch OLED screen with Super Retina XDR technology, providing sharp image quality, accurate color reproduction, high contrast, and economical deep blacks. more battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292420-102459.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Giải trí trên màn hình OLED Super Retina XDR sắc nét | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292420-102459.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292420-102459.jpg\" title=\"Giải trí trên màn hình OLED Super Retina XDR sắc nét | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides, bad news for iFan, iPhone 12 Pro Max will most likely not come with any accessories, including charging cables which are the most basic accessories. This means that users need to spend a fair amount of money to buy genuine products.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The rear camera cluster has been strongly upgraded</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The iPhone 12 Pro Max camera cluster continues to be the most anticipated part as well as the important part that Apple focuses on upgrading through generations <a href=\"https://www.topzone.vn/iphone\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPhone phones being sold at Mobile World brand TopZone\">iPhone phones</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iPhone 12 Pro Max still uses the square camera system on the back and adds a LiDAR sensor to create a quality 3-camera system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-3-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Cụm 3 camera sau cùng cảm biến LiDAR đẳng cấp | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-3-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-3-1.jpg\" title=\"Cụm 3 camera sau cùng cảm biến LiDAR đẳng cấp | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>LiDAR sensor measures laser depth similar to the iPad Pro, helping to accurately identify the distance between objects, enhancing virtual reality applications and also supporting 3 cameras to operate optimally. the best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292720-102707.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Quét mọi vật thể chính xác với cảm biến LiDAR | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292720-102707.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292720-102707.jpg\" title=\"Quét mọi vật thể chính xác với cảm biến LiDAR | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The image quality produced by the iPhone 12 Pro Max is always among the top today with strengths being extremely realistic colors, high accuracy, and a wide color range.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of features, iPhone 12 Pro Max inherits everything currently available on iPhone 11, including Deep Fusion mode and Night Mode. It&#39;s also possible that Apple will add new image processing features.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-9-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Giao diện camera | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-9-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-9-1.jpg\" title=\"Giao diện camera | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, the front camera on iPhone 12 Pro Max with 12MP resolution, supports HDR, Full HD video recording, significantly increases the quality of selfie photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292820-102824.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera selfie 12 MP cũng trang bị đầy đủ tính năng hấp dẫn | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292820-102824.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-292820-102824.jpg\" title=\"Camera selfie 12 MP cũng trang bị đầy đủ tính năng hấp dẫn | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Huge performance from the &quot;monster&quot; A14 Bionic</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A14 Bionic will be the processor found on the iPhone 12 Pro Max with 6 cores clocked up to 3.1 GHz, promising the strongest performance ever on Apple devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-9-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Chip A14 Bionic mạnh mẽ | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-9-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-9-2.jpg\" title=\"Chip A14 Bionic mạnh mẽ | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the device will come with 6 GB RAM to help the device operate smoothly and multitask comfortably. Although a bit late, the A14 finally has a built-in 5G modem, providing the fastest connection today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-293120-103117.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hỗ trợ kết nối 5G siêu nhanh | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-293120-103117.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/213033/iphone-12-pro-max-293120-103117.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ kết nối 5G siêu nhanh | iPhone 12 Pro Max\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this amount of quality and powerful equipment, it is easy to help <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-choi-game\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to electric models gaming phone at Mobile World\">gaming phone</a> is good at all types of games from light to heavy at high configuration levels without any problems.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'iphone-12-pro-max-phone', '2024-12-09 17:29:11', '2024-12-09 17:29:11', NULL),
(72, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G phone', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-512gb-5g\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G 512GB phone at Mobile World\">Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G 512GB</a> when launched, it created a market fever, the outstanding feature is Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 for Galaxy chip and 200 MP camera with integrated AI. This phone model promises to stand out in 2024 with its power and many top-notch features.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Luxury design combined with high-quality Titanium material</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With Galaxy S24 Ultra, the inheritance from the previous generation is not only maintenance but also perfection. The square design with 90-degree corners is an important highlight, creating a unique and classy image. You will feel the luxury and sophistication at first sight. This is not only a change in design but also an inheritance of the essence from previous versions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-3.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế đặc trung của dòng S - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-3.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế đặc trung của dòng S - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This year, Samsung has taken a new step forward in materials by using Titanium for the frame. This not only creates a sturdy appearance but also increases the durability of the device. The frame is mixed with other alloys, creating a work of digital art that is not only durable but also classy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The frame is designed to be slightly curved at the intersection of the back, screen and surrounding frame, optimizing the holding experience by providing comfort and stability. The matte glass back not only increases aesthetics but also ensures durability and elegance. This is a step forward in optimizing quality and user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-9.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Khung làm từ chất liệu mới - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-9.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-9.jpg\" title=\"Khung làm từ chất liệu mới - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compared to previous generations, this year&#39;s Galaxy S24 Ultra becomes more square and luxurious. Every detail is carefully cared for, from the edges to the slender lines, creating an overall look that is not only classy but also a symbol of elegance and modernity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The phone is equipped with an S Pen, which is not just a simple writing and drawing tool but a great assistant for creative lovers. With high sensitivity and many special features, users can freely turn their ideas into reality on the screen. Quick to integrate and easy to use, the S Pen delivers an unprecedented creative experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-10.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trang bị bút S - Pen - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-10.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-10.jpg\" title=\"Trang bị bút S - Pen - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The S Pen is not limited to writing and drawing, but is also a diverse interaction tool. This includes controlling slideshows, taking photos remotely, or even navigating within photography apps. The flexibility of the S Pen creates a unique and more convenient user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Large screen with high brightness up to 2600 nits</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy S24 Ultra&#39;s Dynamic AMOLED 2X panel is not just a breakthrough, but a new standard in mobile image quality. This technology not only provides outstanding brightness and contrast, but also reproduces colors with stunning accuracy, delivering a world of vivid and realistic images.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a large size of up to 6.8 inches, the screen of <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the phone at Mobile World\">phone</a> not only opens up a large space for mobile entertainment but also brings more comfortable movie watching, gaming and web browsing experiences than ever before. In addition, the large size also facilitates users to work easily, especially for quick notes and sketches.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-14.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình lớn sử dụng tấm nền cao cấp - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-14.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-14.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình lớn sử dụng tấm nền cao cấp - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With Quad HD+ resolution, Galaxy S24 Ultra gives users an unlimited visual experience. Every pixel on the screen is reproduced with stunning precision, creating a vivid and sharp world. Whether you&#39;re viewing a still picture or watching high-quality video, this resolution ensures every detail is displayed clearly and realistically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the same time, with a brightness of 2600 nits, the Galaxy S24 Ultra&#39;s screen does not hesitate to face difficult lighting conditions. From now on, users can both view the map and move outdoors without having to worry about difficulty reading or glare.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-16.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Độ sáng màn hình 2600 nits - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-16.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-16.jpg\" title=\"Độ sáng màn hình 2600 nits - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The flexible screen refresh rate feature in the range of 1-120 Hz is a significant step forward, providing a smooth and flexible experience. With adaptive capabilities, the display self-adjusts the refresh rate to optimize performance and save energy, while keeping every image and movement on the screen smooth and natural.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ray Tracing is an advanced 3D graphics technology, often appearing in the gaming and movie industries. On the Galaxy S24 Ultra, Ray Tracing is integrated into the mobile experience, helping to create realistic and detailed lighting effects from every viewing angle. This not only increases the intensity of detail but also makes every image and video come alive and engaging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-24.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tích hợp nhiều tính năng hiện đại - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-24.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-24.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp nhiều tính năng hiện đại - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vision Booster is a smart feature on Galaxy S24 Ultra, which optimizes the brightness and color of the screen based on the surrounding environment. This feature automatically adjusts image parameters, helping users experience high-quality images anytime, anywhere, even in difficult lighting conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>200 MP camera improves photo quality</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung continues to conquer the smartphone market with the Galaxy S24 Ultra, a technological masterpiece that combines classy design and a powerful camera system, bringing the photography and video recording experience to a new level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most special feature of the Galaxy S24 Ultra is the main camera with a resolution of up to 200 MP. This power not only ensures every shot is sharp and detailed down to every pixel, but also opens up a new world of high-resolution photography, highlighting ultimate beauty from every angle.&lt; /p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-6.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trang bị camera 200 MP - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-6.jpg\" title=\"Trang bị camera 200 MP - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comes with a 12 MP ultra-wide-angle camera, helping users expand their vision and capture panoramic views vividly. From natural scenes to party shots, every scene is captured with impressive breadth and quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The telephoto camera system of the Galaxy S24 Ultra is no less impressive with 2 sensors of 10 MP and 50 MP respectively. 3x and 5x optical zoom offers flexibility and variety in remote shooting, keeping every detail clear without sacrificing image quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-7.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera hỗ trợ zoom quang học - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-7.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-7.jpg\" title=\"Camera hỗ trợ zoom quang học - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, Samsung also introduces the &quot;Standard Optical Zoom&quot; feature with two modes 2x and 10x, allowing users to take detailed and unique portrait photos at every moment. The &quot;Instant Motion Recording&quot; feature takes video recording to the next level. Combined with artificial intelligence, Galaxy S24 Ultra not only captures motion with faster operations but also creates smooth and vivid videos, highlighting every memorable moment in life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-13.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tính năng quay chuyển động tức thì - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-13.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-13.jpg\" title=\"Tính năng quay chuyển động tức thì - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Night photography features on the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-chup-anh-shoot-phim\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference Check out mobile phones for photography and videography at Mobile World\">this camera and video phone</a> uses advanced technology, helping to capture every detail in low light conditions. Now every night photo is vivid and clear, naturally highlighting the beauty of the night scene.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Optical image stabilization (OIS) technology on the Galaxy S24 Ultra camera helps stabilize images, especially in low light conditions or when shooting from a distance. Thanks to OIS, every photo is captured with high sharpness and detail, without blur or shaking. RAW photography allows users to store original images in an uncompressed format, retaining all detailed information. This provides great flexibility when editing photos after shooting, while preserving the best quality from each photo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-22.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tối ưu ảnh chụp sắc nét - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-22.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-22.jpg\" title=\"Tối ưu ảnh chụp sắc nét - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Peak performance thanks to Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 for Galaxy chip</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With the use of Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 for Galaxy chip, the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference This Samsung phone at Mobile World\">Samsung phone</a> takes the phone experience to a new level. The powerful performance of this chip not only helps the phone run smoothly and quickly, but also highlights its ability to handle multitasking and resource-demanding applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 for Galaxy chip is not just about performance, but also focuses on artificial intelligence (AI). This enhances the ability to process information in real time, from improving user experience to intervening in the camera to make photography better and smarter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-18.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tích hợp chipset cấu hình cao - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-18.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-18.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp chipset cấu hình cao - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-choi-game\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to high-configuration phones at Mobile World \">This high-configuration phone</a> is equipped with large RAM up to 12 GB, ensuring all operations are smooth and fast. This not only helps open multitasking flexibly but also responds well to applications and games that require large resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-17.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tích hợp chipset cấu hình cao - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-17.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-17.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp chipset cấu hình cao - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The storage space of the Galaxy S24 Ultra is also very impressive. You can choose the version with 512 GB of internal memory, or if you are someone with more or less large storage needs, there are two more options of 256 GB and 1 TB. This means you have enough space to store all your memorable moments, high-quality videos, and favorite apps without having to worry about memory limitations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Integrating smart features</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Versatile search area</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy S24 Ultra possesses a versatile search feature, allowing users to quickly find information anytime, anywhere. You just need to draw an area on the screen and the phone will automatically search for that area, saving time and improving work efficiency.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Khoang vùng tìm kiếm đa năng - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-2.jpg\" title=\"Khoang vùng tìm kiếm đa năng - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smart photo editing assistant</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adding the smart photo editing assistant feature, Galaxy S24 Ultra not only helps you take beautiful photos but also provides photo editing suggestions to bring the best results. This feature is a powerful assistant, accompanying you in making each photo impressive and vivid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-12-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trợ lý chỉnh ảnh thông minh - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-12-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-12-1.jpg\" title=\"Trợ lý chỉnh ảnh thông minh - Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Create smart wallpapers and smart browsers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy S24 Ultra takes user experience to a new level with smart wallpaper creation and smart browsing. The system automatically adjusts the wallpaper based on your preferences and environment, and the smart browser helps you browse the web efficiently and flexibly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Direct call interpretation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the live call translation feature, Galaxy S24 Ultra is not only a regular phone but also a multilingual communication tool. Conversations become faster and more convenient, making the connection between listener and speaker smoother than ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-23.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Phiên dịch trực tiếp cuộc gọi - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-23.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-23.jpg\" title=\"Phiên dịch trực tiếp cuộc gọi - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Touchless communication assistant</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Additional touchless communication assistant feature, Galaxy S24 Ultra allows users to adjust the phone by voice, making driving and customizing maps easier. Through voice commands, you can perform tasks without touching the screen, providing a more comfortable and secure user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Equipped with a built-in huge battery with super fast charging 2.0 technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most notable features of the Galaxy S24 Ultra is its large battery with a capacity of 5000 mAh. This not only ensures that the phone has enough energy to operate throughout the day but also meets the needs of users who love technology. Enjoy every moment without worrying about constantly charging the battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-19.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trang bị viên pin khủng - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-19.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/307174/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-19.jpg\" title=\"Trang bị viên pin khủng - Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy S24 Ultra&#39;s super fast charging 2.0 technology with a capacity of 45 W takes the charging experience to a new level. Just a few minutes of connecting to the charger, you will have enough power for a long time of use. This is not only a time saver but also a great convenience, especially when you need to use your phone quickly in emergencies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In summary, this phone is the top choice for those who love technology and are looking for a versatile device that fully meets all usage needs. Expected to attract attention in the near future, the Galaxy S24 Ultra is truly an excellent product for 2024.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-5g-phone', '2024-12-09 17:29:29', '2024-12-09 17:29:29', NULL);
