(73, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G phone', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB phone at Di Gioi Di Dynamic\">Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB</a> is Samsung&#39;s most high-end smartphone, possessing an unbelievable configuration with a powerful chip developed by Qualcomm optimized exclusively for the Galaxy series and camera up to 200 MP, worthy of being the most anticipated Android flagship in 2023.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Integrated AI features</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy S23 Ultra made a strong impression when launched with its groundbreaking design and outstanding performance. In late March 2024, Samsung introduced One UI 6.1, bringing to the Galaxy S23 Ultra advanced AI features from the previous Galaxy S24 series.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/42/324028/Samsung-ho-tro-ai-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/42/324028/Samsung-ho-tro-ai-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/42/324028/Samsung-ho-tro-ai-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ AI\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Users can experience Smart Note Assistant, Photo Editing Assistant, Smart Chat Assistant, Live Interpretation and Smart Search Localization, all of which increase convenience and user experience mobile devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Creating a luxurious and sophisticated image</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of design, the Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra will continue to inherit the luxurious design from the previous generation, still with a metal frame, glass back and slightly curved shape on the sides and screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020326.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế sang trọng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020326.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020326.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế sang trọng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, this curved style will tend to be a bit flat compared to the S22 Ultra, this gives me a firmer grip experience, but also brings a comfortable feeling for continuous use. for a long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of color, this year Samsung has also released color versions such as: Purple, cream, blue and black. In general, these are extremely luxurious and elegant colors, suitable for active, strong young people and especially business customers because of their classy and elegant appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently in my hand is Samsung&#39;s signature blue version, this color both brings fresh youthfulness and also carries a dark color scheme to maintain a mysterious and enchanting look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020336.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màu sắc mê hoặc - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020336.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020336.jpg\" title=\"Màu sắc mê hoặc - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the back, we can see that Samsung has equipped the device with a layer of tempered glass with good impact resistance, made in a slightly rough style, making fingerprints almost invisible during use. I experienced it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020340.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Mặt lưng kính nhám - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020340.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020340.jpg\" title=\"Mặt lưng kính nhám - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of camera design, this year the company has almost no changes compared to the Galaxy S22 Ultra, the camera cluster is still arranged individually and raised quite high.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, a layer of border will be added around the lenses that is higher than the camera surface, this helps limit scratches on the lens surface very well, so I also feel more secure while using it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020347.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Vị trí camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020347.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020347.jpg\" title=\"Vị trí camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the edges around the device, the Galaxy S23 Ultra is surrounded by a frame made of aluminum with durable, sturdy properties and extremely effectively optimized weight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This frame is made in a glossy style, giving the device an additional highlight in design. The feeling when touching the frame is like being covered with a layer of glossy plating around it, so this will not be an easy place to scratch as some users suspect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020353.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Khung viền bo cong - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020353.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020353.jpg\" title=\"Khung viền bo cong - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Performance beyond all limits</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At the time of product launch, the Galaxy S23 Ultra can be considered a <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?g=android\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference Android phones doing business at Mobile World\">Android phones</a> have the most powerful performance on the market. This is because Samsung has equipped the advanced Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 chip specifically optimized by Qualcomm for the Galaxy S series product line, providing superior performance compared to the regular Snapdragon 8 Gen 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First of all, about the basic experience with tasks such as: Watching movies, surfing the web, taking photos or making calls and texting, it seems that the device does not encounter any difficulties at all, everything is performed. out smoothly and extremely smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020358.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiệu năng mượt mà - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020358.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020358.jpg\" title=\"Hiệu năng mượt mà - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To be able to evaluate the phone&#39;s configuration more intuitively with numbers, I also tested a few performance testing software with the following results: 1767 (single core ), 4314 (multi-core) on Geekbench 6 and 15635 points on PCMark.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020403.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Điểm đánh giá hiệu năng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020403.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020403.jpg\" title=\"Điểm đánh giá hiệu năng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the present time (April 2023), these are indeed very high numbers and there are few models with such a high score. Thanks to that, the Galaxy S23 Ultra can confidently handle any task well at this time, or even provide a smooth usage experience for up to 2 - 3 years or longer depending on the purpose of use. use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coming to the gaming experience, Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 for Galaxy seems to have the opportunity to reveal most of the chip&#39;s power, this is proven when I play through games like Lien Quan Mobile and Lien Quan Mobile. Genshin Impact at the highest graphics level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020407.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020407.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020407.jpg\" title=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Lien Quan Mobile, the device allows setting the maximum graphics level through the following levels: Super high resolution, HD image quality and high detail quality. This contributes to increasing your gaming experience when all content is displayed at its best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020412.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Bảng cài dặt cấu hình - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020412.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020412.jpg\" title=\"Bảng cài dặt cấu hình - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>After about 2 consecutive games on the Galaxy S23 Ultra, I found that the device does not seem to experience any lag or slowness, even during team fights, when all visual effects from all All champions are displayed at almost the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020646.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020646.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020646.jpg\" title=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The chart recording the frame rate when playing Lien Quan at this time shows that everything is going very well, there are no fluctuations or drops too deep to cause lag, FPS always fluctuates during the game. about 59 - 64.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020642.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020642.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020642.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next is the game Genshin Impact which is a bit more difficult, the configuration level I set for the device at this time is almost the highest. This can be considered an unbelievable level of graphics, which can only be installed and works well on high-end devices like the Galaxy S23 Ultra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020653.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020653.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020653.jpg\" title=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through practical experience, I find that the Galaxy S23 Ultra handles this game very well, although there is only a slight delay while loading the map at the beginning, but it is not anything too big. influence your experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Everything right now is handled well by the Galaxy S23 Ultra, the frame rate always fluctuates stably in the range of 27 - 31 FPS, I feel the image display is very smooth, all character navigation operations also responded quickly and there was almost no delay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020659.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020659.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020659.jpg\" title=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>About the issue of heat generation when using <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to mobile phones being sold at Mobile World \">phone</a> in advanced tasks, the Galaxy S23 Ultra seems to have optimized this part very well, while I played the game at high settings continuously for 2 hours, with wifi connection, brightness Average screen and performance in lips When the temperature is 26 - 27 degrees, the machine still produces low heat, seemingly only stopping at a light hand-warming level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020704.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020704.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020704.jpg\" title=\"Trải nghiệm chơi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Is a <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-8gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to 8GB RAM phones being sold at Mobile World\">8 GB RAM phone</a>, Galaxy S23 Ultra can fully handle multitasking tasks effectively and quickly, with about 15 - 18 applications (except games) open at the same time then later After about 20 minutes of reopening, the device still did not appear to reload the application from the beginning and this was also something I was very surprised about when using it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020709.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Đa nhiệm mượt mà - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020709.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020709.jpg\" title=\"Đa nhiệm mượt mà - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Equiped with a 200 MP camera and 8K video recording capability</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Regarding the lens system, the Galaxy S23 Ultra is equipped with 4 cameras on the back with parameters: 200 MP for the main camera, a 12 MP super wide-angle camera and two telephoto cameras with the same 10-megapixel resolution. MP to support optical zoom photography and background blur.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First, it will be the default shooting mode in outdoor conditions. In a well-lit environment, the results I get are very satisfying, everything shows detail, colors are enhanced. Light tones help the photo look fresher and more vibrant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020721.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020721.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020721.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the results, I can completely use it immediately to post on social networks without having to go through many post-production steps. In addition, you can also use many other color filter options. to find the most suitable color scheme for the scene or topic you are aiming for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next will be the super wide-angle shooting mode. In this feature, the device allows you to capture photos with a large coverage, resulting in almost everything captured. appear before my eyes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020727.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020727.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020727.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In places around the extended border, there will be no distortion, and the level of detail is also guaranteed to help the photo look more realistic and artistic, so I feel very satisfied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So far, Samsung&#39;s flagship phones have always been considered devices with extremely good optical zoom capabilities in photography, and this will repeat again on the Galaxy S23 Ultra. when the device supports up to 2 telephoto sensors to support 10X and 3X optical zoom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the zoom photos, I really don&#39;t feel that there is too much change in detail between photos taken with the telephoto camera compared to the main camera, everything is very realistic and clear, overall. The photo looks harmonious from color to light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020735.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020735.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020735.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>*Photo taken from super wide-angle mode</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021023.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021023.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021023.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>*Photo taken from default mode</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021030.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021030.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021030.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>*Photo taken from 3X zoom mode</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One point that I felt very impressed while taking zoom photos on the Galaxy S23 Ultra was the ability to focus and shoot speed. Maybe you also know that when we take zoom photos, the camera&#39;s camera is susceptible to slow focus, shaking or blurry photos, but on this S23 Ultra phone, this has been almost completely overcome. .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021035.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021035.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021035.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>*Photo taken from 10X zoom mode</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021042.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021042.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021042.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>*Photo taken from 10X zoom mode</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For someone like me who often takes outdoor photos, I think the light processing ability on the S23 Ultra works extremely effectively, even when shooting facing the sun when it&#39;s sunny, the camera still has the ability to handle light. Well balanced, the relationship between the subject and the bright area behind are all harmoniously balanced to make the picture extremely beautiful.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021048.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021048.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021048.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The next interesting point I want to share about the S23 Ultra&#39;s camera is in the color processing, as usual on models <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd -samsung\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung phones being sold at Mobile World\">Samsung phones</a>, the photos taken will tend to have more vibrant color tones. Take a moment to let the picture turn should be more lively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021053.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021053.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021053.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021059.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021059.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021059.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, this can also be considered a limitation for some specific situations. In fact, the S23 Ultra handles most colors well, however, in hot colors, the machine processes a bit too much, so often the colors will no longer be very realistic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021107.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021107.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021107.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moving to night conditions, the Galaxy S23 Ultra seems to demonstrate the power of the camera and prove why it is called the &quot;Eye of the God of Darkness&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Actually speaking, the ability to capture light and process images on this camera is extremely good, the light sources during night shooting will not be blurred or glare, the noise phenomenon is also improved compared to with the previous generation helps make the photo more harmonious and flattering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021113.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021113.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021113.jpg\" title=\"Ảnh chụp từ camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An equally impressive point is the video recording feature on the camera with a maximum recording standard of up to 8K at a frame rate of 30 fps, this will bring us cinematic footage when The resolution obtained now is extremely large.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Convenient integrated S-Pen</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Similar to the sample <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung-galaxy-s\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Galaxy S series phones doing business in the World Mobile World\">Previous Galaxy S series phone</a>, S23 Ultra will also continue to be equipped with the legendary S-Pen right in the body of the device, this can be considered something that customers in the user object is Businessmen or creative people love it because of its convenience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regarding the feeling of pressing to take out the pen, I find it quite easy. Just lightly touch the area containing the pen and this accessory will immediately push out so I can pull it out easily.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021118.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tích hợp bút S-Pen - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021118.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021118.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp bút S-Pen - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For someone like me who does content creation work, the S-Pen will be very suitable for me to perform tasks such as sketching drawing content, creating signatures, taking quick notes or even You can use it to perform video editing tasks. The small tip will help you edit and cut videos more accurately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the latency of the pen, I don&#39;t seem to feel it during use, everything responds quickly and almost perfectly matches my operations (when at the scanning frequency). 120 Hz screen), so I also feel very comfortable using the S-Pen and it seems to become an indispensable part while I work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021445.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tích hợp bút S-Pen - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021445.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021445.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp bút S-Pen - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Large screen brings endless space</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Galaxy S23 Ultra, Samsung has integrated into this device many outstanding parameters, specifically Dynamic AMOLED 2X screen technology, 2K+ resolution (1440 x 3088 Pixels) and maximum brightness. 1750 nits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/tim-hieu-man-hinh-dynamic-amoled-2x-tren-smartphone-1245213\" target=\"_blank\">What is Dynamic AMOLED 2X display? Highlights? Available on any phone</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>All three of these things provide display quality with vibrant colors, and content is also reproduced more sharply when playing games or watching movies. Above all, the high brightness will also help you in viewing maps on the street or adjusting photography angles when using in high-light environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021459.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Độ sáng màn hình cao - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021459.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021459.jpg\" title=\"Độ sáng màn hình cao - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>More interestingly, the high resolution on the S23 Ultra allows you to set a higher resolution when viewing content, helping to fully enjoy the beauty of the frame in the most vivid way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the use of a large 6.8 inch screen, every movie I watch is shown in a larger size, the space has now become spacious for all gestures and operations with the S-pen. My pen becomes comfortable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021504.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Không gian hiển thị rõ ràng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021504.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-021504.jpg\" title=\"Không gian hiển thị rõ ràng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" /></a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-5g-phone', '2024-12-09 17:29:43', '2024-12-09 17:29:43', NULL),
(74, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G phone', NULL, '<h3>The impressive return of the super product <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 at Thegioididong.com\">Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6</a>, continues to symbolize Samsung&#39;s innovation and creativity in the smartphone field. With outstanding improvements in design, higher configuration, more &quot;genuine&quot; features and still retaining the impressive folding and opening style for multitasking and handling tasks of modern users.<!-- h3--></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Classy folding style</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold6 not only inherits the unique folding design from previous versions but is also significantly improved in overall thinness and volume. With a thickness of 12.1 mm when folded and 5.6 mm when opened, with a weight of 239g, Z Fold6 becomes lighter and easier to carry than ever. Furthermore, this innovative design also makes the surface neater and much easier to hold.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-13.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Thiết kế\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-13.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-13.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Thiết kế\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The hinge uses the familiar Flex Hinge technology on the previous Z Fold5 line, designed with a special dual groove mechanism, helping to improve the ability to open and close smoothly, firmly and limit folds that cause damage. uncomfortable vision during the experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Increased flexibility to switch between different usage modes, fully open to experience movies, folded to use like a regular phone or the &quot;exclusive&quot; Flex Mode feature on the line <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung-galaxy-z\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy Z phone models at thegioididong.com\">phone Samsung Galaxy Z</a> supports adjusting brightness, sound, screen capture,... just like a smartphone <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business laptops at Thegioididong.com\">laptop</a> miniature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-9-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Gập mở\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-9-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-9-1.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Gập mở\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold6 is flexible and convertible with a thinner design and lighter weight, but still retains reliable durability. The aluminum metal frame is improved, the screen is equipped with a tempered layer and IP48 standard, making the device more resistant to dust and water than previous generations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Outstanding power with breakthrough chip</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold6 is equipped with Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 for Galaxy processor, developed on a 4 nm process, providing outstanding performance and optimal energy savings. Compared to the previous generation (Galaxy Z Fold5), the device&#39;s performance has improved by more than 18%, helping the device handle daily tasks smoothly and quickly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The graphics capabilities of the GPU on the chip have been significantly improved by 19% compared to the previous generation, helping to smoothly handle high-configuration games, effectively fine-tune graphics and perform any tasks. any service you want on your mobile device without hindrance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320722/samsung-galaxy-z-flip6-13.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Chip\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320722/samsung-galaxy-z-flip6-13.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320722/samsung-galaxy-z-flip6-13.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Flip6 5G 12GB/256GB - Hiệu năng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 12 GB of RAM, Galaxy Z Fold6 allows you to perform multiple tasks at the same time quickly and smoothly. Large cache helps you not have to waste time reloading web pages or applications when opening them to continue working.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-8-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Ứng dụng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-8-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-8-1.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Ứng dụng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Smart AI features</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6, the latest in the Galaxy product line, is equipped with advanced AI features through the One UI 6.1 interface. These features include a smart note assistant for effective note management. Photo editing assistant recommends suitable filters, effects and edits to create professional photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-12.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Trợ lý AI\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-12.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-12.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Trợ lý AI\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Integrated Google Gemini Chat to find creative ideas for all types of content. In addition, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung phone models at thegioididong.com\">phone Samsung</a> also has a smart search feature, allowing you to easily find related information with a few simple steps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-10.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Khoanh vùng tìm kiếm \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-10.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-10.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Khoanh vùng tìm kiếm \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With these AI features, Galaxy Z Fold6 is not only powerful in hardware but also brings a convenient and smart experience, helping users perform daily tasks effectively with little effort. out the most.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Double your experience with a premium screen</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A noticeable highlight in the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?g=android\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to samples Android phone at thegioididong.com\">Samsung&#39;s Android phone</a> is a Dynamic AMOLED 2X screen, with high color contrast and accurate, realistic image reproduction. This brings an extremely attractive and interesting usage and entertainment experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.6-inch main screen with QXGA+ resolution (1856 x 2160 Pixels) allows displaying all images, videos and multimedia content with high detail. Furthermore, the size is as large as a phone. <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business tablets at Thegioididong.com\"> This small tablet</a> also supports displaying content in multiple windows, a more eye-catching movie experience, or dividing the display in half for many different tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-2-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Màn hình chính\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-2-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-2-1.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Màn hình chính\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>120 Hz scanning frequency ensures every step of converting applications and software is as smooth as possible. In addition, experiencing racing and shooting games on high-speed frames also becomes smooth, completely eye-catching without being caught in cases of tearing or interruption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 6.3-inch outer screen of the Galaxy Z Fold6 is slightly larger than the previous generations of Z Fold5 and Z Fold4. Equipped with Dynamic AMOLED 2X technology and HD+ resolution (968 x 2376 Pixels), this screen delivers detailed and sharp images for all displayed content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-5.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Màn hình ngoài\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-5.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Màn hình ngoài\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In general, with this external monitor, users still own all the features or toolsets like a popular phone, ready to convert to meet personal needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Impressive personal photography</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold6 owns a rear camera system with the highest resolution up to 50 MP, supporting OIS anti-shake features, optical zoom, night mode,... preserving image color highest in different lighting conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-17.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Camera \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-17.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-17.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Camera \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 2x and 3x optical zoom while still reducing noise and maintaining clear resolution thanks to ProVisual Engine - the Galaxy AI integration tool, you can easily capture every moment in high detail. right in the frame.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-11.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Thu phóng quang học \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-11.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-11.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Thu phóng quang học \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the camera on the Galaxy Z Fold6 also supports 8K video recording, suitable for multimedia content creators, allowing high-quality video recording and editing directly on <a href=\"https ://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to phone models at thegioididong.com\">phone</a> without the need for support tools bulky aid other.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>All-day flexibility with large battery capacity</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The phone is equipped with a 4400 mAh battery, energy-saving chip and optimized performance. With smart battery management, users can use the phone for a long time before needing to recharge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Pin\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/320721/samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-acv-2.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Z Fold6 5G - Pin\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The specific battery life will depend on usage, but under normal conditions it can maintain full operation for a day. According to the company, the Galaxy Z Fold6&#39;s battery has a battery life that can play audio for up to 77 hours and video for up to 23 hours, slightly better than the 73 and 21 hours of the older brother Z Fold5.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-z-fold6-5g-phone', '2024-12-09 17:29:58', '2024-12-09 17:29:58', NULL);
