(75, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 5G phone', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-5g-512gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 5G 512GB at World Mobile World\">Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 5G 512GB</a> was also officially launched in July 2023 with a breakthrough powerful, opening up new flexible experiences through unique folding capabilities, large sharp screens, outstanding performance for optimal multitasking capabilities and many other attractive features to meet the requirements higher from users.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>AI feature support</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold5, Samsung&#39;s outstanding large smartphone, after its successful launch, has now become smarter through AI features inherited from the Galaxy S24 series introduced by Samsung through One UI 6.1 at the end of March 2024.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/42/324028/Samsung-ho-tro-ai-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/42/324028/Samsung-ho-tro-ai-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/42/324028/Samsung-ho-tro-ai-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ AI\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features include: &quot;Smart Note Assistant&quot; for efficient note-taking, &quot;Photo Editing Assistant&quot; for professional image editing, &quot;Smart Chat Assistant&quot; for marking important tasks from conversation, &quot;Live Interpretation&quot; for skillful communication and &quot;Smart search zoning&quot; for easier information finding.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Flexible folding hinge design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 continues to elevate the unique folding design of the previous Galaxy Z Fold series, bringing a remarkable and memorable mobile experience. With innovation and new features, this phone brings a clear difference compared to previous versions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung has focused on optimizing the size and weight of the Galaxy Z Fold5, making the phone lighter and easier to store in your pocket or bag. When opened, you will experience a large screen, providing a large and impressive space for viewing content and working.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095313.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095313.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095313.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite its slim design, the Galaxy Z Fold5 has no problems with durability and stability. This is ensured thanks to the careful integration of the hinge and the use of sturdy materials during the design. Users can feel confident and secure when using their phone every day without worrying about the thinness that can affect the durability of the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095321.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095321.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095321.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The highlight of the Galaxy Z Fold5 is the specially designed Flex hinge, ensuring stability and smooth opening and closing. Samsung has invested in research and development to improve and optimize the hinge, helping to fold and open easily and avoid unwanted folds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095317.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095317.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095317.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Experience premium gaming with Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 for Galaxy</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Another difference is that the powerful Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 for Galaxy processor is integrated into the Galaxy Z Fold5, ensuring optimal performance and smooth multitasking. With this advanced processor, you can perform many complex tasks quickly and efficiently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095950.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiệu năng điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095950.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095950.jpg\" title=\"Hiệu năng điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With fast clock speeds and optimal multitasking capabilities, users will experience smoothness and quick response in every task, from opening applications, watching multimedia content, Come play your favorite games. Compared to the previous version, there have been significant improvements in performance, while optimizing the software and hardware of <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?g=android\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Android phones at Mobile World\">this Android phone</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100115.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiệu năng điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100115.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100115.jpg\" title=\"Hiệu năng điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Use Dynamic AMOLED 2X screen</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With the use of multi-touch Dynamic AMOLED 2X panels, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 phone at Thegioididong.com\">Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5</a> has brought out the colors with great realism and sharpness. This panel&#39;s high-resolution reproduction and remarkable contrast deliver vivid and realistic content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095632.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095632.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095632.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With high QXGA+ resolution, the Galaxy Z Fold5 screen ensures excellent detail when viewing images, videos and other multimedia content. Clear and sharp images full of details promise to bring a more wonderful and engaging content viewing experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High screen scanning frequency of up to 120 Hz is also a notable point of Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5. The experience is smooth, flicker-free and responsive especially when swiping and tapping the screen. Switches between apps and websites are smooth and easy, along with a smooth and realistic gaming experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095638.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095638.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095638.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The external screen of the Galaxy Z Fold5 also uses Dynamic AMOLED 2X technology with a size of 6.2 inches, providing sharp and high-contrast display images, creating an incredible content viewing experience.&lt; /p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095700.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Màn hình điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095700.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-095700.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The HD+ secondary screen resolution provides clear and sharp quality for images, videos and multimedia content, good enough for you to comfortably watch movies and play games. All of these things together make the Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 outstanding and attractive in the smartphone market.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Save every memorable moment</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>An important aspect that makes the Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 stand out is its diverse and powerful camera system. On the back surface, this phone is equipped with three main cameras with outstanding photography capabilities, including a main lens with high resolution up to 50 MP, a 12 MP ultra-wide camera and a 10 MP telephoto camera that supports the function OIS function for long zoom shooting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100606.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera của điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100606.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100606.jpg\" title=\"Camera của điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The front screen of the phone is not inferior either, it is equipped with a pair of cameras including a 10 MP selfie camera (when folded) and a 4 MP camera (when opened to full screen). Thanks to these cameras, you will comfortably take selfies or participate in video calls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only that, the Galaxy Z Fold5&#39;s camera system also supports many special features such as Night Mode, allowing you to take photos with excellent quality even in low light environments, helps you capture memorable moments at night without worrying about blurry or noisy image quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100611.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera của điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100611.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100611.jpg\" title=\"Camera của điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Large battery enough for all day use</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold5 is equipped with a 4400 mAh battery with advanced technology to help prolong life and increase load capacity compared to previous versions. With a large capacity battery and optimal power efficiency, the phone promises to provide continuous use for a long time before needing to be recharged.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even with normal usage such as surfing the web, watching videos and using daily applications, users will enjoy 7-10 hours before the battery drains, reducing the hassle associated with charging the battery too often.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100742.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Pin trên điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100742.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/301608/samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-260723-100742.jpg\" title=\"Pin trên điện thoại - Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Z Fold5 also has a built-in fast charging feature via Type-C port, supporting maximum power up to 25 W. With Samsung&#39;s advanced fast charging technology, refilling the battery becomes quick. and users can continue to use the phone without having to wait long.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides that, the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung phones at Mobile World\">Samsung phones </a> also supports convenient wireless charging, helping users easily charge the battery without complicated cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In short, Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 5G 512GB brings a difference and elevates the mobile experience with a unique folding design, powerful performance, stunning screen and the ability to take quality photos and videos. High. This phone is truly a new step forward in mobile technology and promises to bring users memorable and wonderful experiences.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-z-fold5-5g-phone', '2024-12-09 17:30:11', '2024-12-09 17:30:11', NULL),
(76, 2, 'Laptop Apple MacBook Air 13 inch M2', NULL, '<h3>After 14 years, three revisions and two different processor architectures, the MacBook Air&#39;s iconic slimmer profile is history. Instead, there is a <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Apple MacBook Air M2 2022 laptop on sale at thegioididong.com\">MacBook Air M2</a> with a completely new design, the same thickness as the MacBook Pro, breaking all barriers with the powerful Apple M2 chip strong.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Spectacular transformation with trendy, luxurious design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Classiness comes from the appearance of the device <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-apple-macbook-air\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more current MacBook Air models doing business at thegioididong.com\">MacBook Air</a> of Apple is undeniable and it is difficult for any product line in the same segment to surpass it. Still a sturdy <strong>full metal shell</strong> <strong>block</strong> with square, luxurious edges, but this year&#39;s MacBook Air 2022 has broken away from the gentle design language. which has been around for a long time and has a new look similar to its &quot;elder&quot; MacBook Pro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112213.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Thiết kế thời thượng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112213.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112213.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Thiết kế thời thượng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The thickness of <strong>11.3 mm</strong> and the impressive weight of <strong>1.24 kg</strong> will be a perfect plus point for mobility, always ready to accompany a user. As a student or office worker like me, going to school or company is also comfortable for creative users and especially for businessmen on long business trips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112217.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Thiết kế sang trọng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112217.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112217.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Thiết kế sang trọng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite its slimmer appearance and lighter weight, the new MacBook Air is still no less sturdy and well-finished than before. The chassis is hard, the lid almost does not bend when I apply force and can still be opened with one finger. Apple is always at the top when it comes to manufacturing quality, and the new Air is no exception.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personally, I really like the color Midnight with a dark blue-black finish that can change depending on the light, but it has a downside because it easily sticks to fingerprints, losing the inherently luxurious appearance of a phone. <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop?g=high-cap-luxury-trong\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more high-end - luxury laptop models currently sold at thegioididong.com\">high-end - luxury laptop</a>, you can choose to buy gray, silver or gold colors that won&#39;t easily attract fingerprints or take the trouble to clean regularly to keep the device shiny.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112207.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Midnight\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112207.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112207.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Midnight\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A clear change in the keyboard <strong>Magic Key</strong> of the line <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-apple-macbook\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more Apple Laptop models currently on sale at thegioididong.com\">Apple laptop</a> This year&#39;s M2 is the size of the F function key row that has been increased to be equal to other key lines, for me history operation used accurately, without confusion. Furthermore, the typing experience is also very gentle, smooth, and the pressing sound is also softer than the old butterfly keyboard. Combined with <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-den-ban-phim\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laptops, laptops equipped with keyboard lights are doing business at Thegioididong .com\">backlight</a> helps me work more easily in many different light and dark conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112231.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Bàn phím\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112231.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112231.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Bàn phím\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Feature <strong>Touch ID</strong> (fingerprint sensor) integrated power button instead of password allows you to quickly unlock the device, access applications and make application payments, No need to waste time or remember passwords like traditional security methods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112234.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Touch ID\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112234.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112234.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Touch ID\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The trackpad isn&#39;t much different from older models although Apple has made it a bit wider, functionally the same with great swiping, gesture support and command rejection when I accidentally put my palm on it. One of the other interesting changes on the new Air is that the speaker grille has been hidden, located on the hinge between the keyboard and screen to keep the appearance neater.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112209.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - TouchPad\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112209.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112209.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - TouchPad\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MacBook Air M2 2022 has the same <strong>MagSafe charging head</strong> as the MacBook Pro 14 and 16, allowing you to charge without worrying about tripping over the cable and causing the computer to fall to the floor. Thanks to the MagSafe port, I actually have an extra USB-C port compared to older models. Instead of having to use one port to charge the computer and the other port for peripherals, I can now use both ports that support Thunderbolt for accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112245.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Cổng MagSafe\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112245.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112245.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Cổng MagSafe\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Break all limits thanks to the power of the Apple M2 processor</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor<a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/chip-apple-m2-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-voi-suc-manh-frame-1437839\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Learn more about the Apple M2 chip \"> Apple M2</a> although similar in structure to the M1, has high performance more than <strong>18%</strong> and <strong>1.9 times</strong> faster than other lines <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laptop | Laptops for sale at Thegioididong.com\">laptop</a> possesses another 10-core processor, more than capable of handling all tasks from studying, working to graphics to specialized engineering. deep. Graphics <strong>8-core GPU</strong> for <strong>35%</strong> more powerful performance, processing up to <strong>15.8 trillion</strong> tasks in <strong> 1 second</strong> so tasks related to images, graphics, videos,... are all handled very smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112236.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Hiệu năng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112236.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112236.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Hiệu năng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s perfect for light video and photo editing, especially if you use Apple&#39;s Photos app or iMovie for those tasks. <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-8-gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more 8 GB RAM Laptop models currently on sale at thegioididong.com\">RAM 8 Laptop GB</a> allows me to use many different application windows at the same time with remarkably smooth multitasking, working on Photoshop while listening to music is still very smooth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112222.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Đa nhiệm\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112222.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112222.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Đa nhiệm\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hard drive space <strong>256 GB SSD</strong> is just enough for documents and learning applications, but because it is only equipped with a single NAND chip instead of two chips like on M1 or M2 models I just have a hard drive of 512 GB or more, so the read and write speed is significantly more limited. I tried measuring the reading speed with the Black Magic Speed ​​Test tool and got 1543 MB/s, nearly half lower than the 2982 MB/s of the MacBook Air M1 256 GB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112239.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Tốc độ SSD\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112239.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112239.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Tốc độ SSD\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I tested the device&#39;s temperature by running heavy tasks at the same time such as rendering videos, opening multiple Safari tabs and running Photoshop, and after a long time the device became noticeably hotter. In my opinion, the reason partly comes from the thinner appearance, in addition to the fact that the heatsink has no fan, so the device heats up quickly which is understandable. In fact, few people use MacBook Air for heavy tasks like the above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112241.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"MacBook Air M2 - Nhiệt độ\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112241.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/282827/apple-macbook-air-m2-2022-161122-112241.jpg\" title=\"MacBook Air M2 - Nhiệt độ\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Owns a battery of <strong>52.6 Wh</strong> but due to its high performance and temperature, the M2 Air has the same battery life as the M1 model, allowing me to use from <strong>8 to 10 hours&lt; /strong&gt; at 200 nits brightness level and various office work tasks. St