\n			<p>Sleep monitoring, Heart rate measurement, Step counting,...</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Training support</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>+100 exercises</td>\r\n			<td>15 exercises</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Bluetooth version</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Bluetooth v5.3</td>\r\n			<td>Bluetooth v5.1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Color</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Pink, Light Gray, Black - Gray</td>\r\n			<td>​Red, Black</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3>Exquisite beauty and convenience</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy Fit3 smart bracelet impresses with its compact design, hugging the wrist, providing maximum comfort to the user. Dynamic, modern appearance and trendy colors create style highlights for both male and female users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Soft, breathable <strong>silicone</strong>material used for the Galaxy Fit 3 strap ensures a smooth and comfortable feeling when worn for long periods of time. Convenient detachable design allows you to easily change the strap according to your preferences and personality, creating your own unique style.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Thiết kế\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-2.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Thiết kế\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Fit3 has a modern <strong>rectangular</strong> face with a size<strong> 40 mm</strong>, similar to a <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong .com/dong-ho-thong-minh\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more smart watch models at Mobile World\">smartwatch</a>. This size is neither too big nor too small, suitable for many user wrist sizes. The four corners of the watch face are delicately curved, creating a harmonious and luxurious overall look. <strong>Aluminum frame</strong> not only provides a high-end appearance but also has good bearing capacity, limiting distortion upon impact.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh?g=vong-tay-thong-minh\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bracelet reference business intelligence at Mobile World\">this smart bracelet</a> is equipped with a <strong>AMOLED </strong>wide <strong>1.6 inch</strong> screen, providing a wide viewing space Large and comfortable market. Resolution <strong>256 x 402 pixels</strong> for sharp images and vivid colors. Thanks to that, you can easily monitor information on Galaxy Fit 3 even under strong light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-3.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Màn hình\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-3.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Màn hình\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Supports scientific and effective training</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Galaxy Fit3 is the ideal companion for your fitness journey. The bracelet is equipped with <strong>more than 100 sports modes</strong> ranging from indoor to outdoor, including walking, jogging, cycling, swimming, climbing,... and many more. Exercises with professional machines help you freely explore and conquer your passion for exercise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, this Samsung smart bracelet can also automatically<strong> track 6 exercises</strong>, making it more convenient for users during the exercise process. After exercising, you can review the indicators on your phone through the Samsung Health application. Based on this information, you can proceed to establish an appropriate exercise and rest plan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-30.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Chế độ thể thao\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-30.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-30.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Chế độ thể thao\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Companion for comprehensive health care</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The house&#39;s smart bracelet model <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/samsung\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung products sold at Thegioididong.com\" type=\"Refer to Samsung products sold at Thegioididong.com\">Samsung</a> is not only an effective training support tool, but also a companion to help you understand more about your health. Through a sensor system and monitoring features, this device gives you a more detailed view of your health status, thereby creating a foundation for scientific adjustments in lifestyle and habits. practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Going beyond function <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-theo-doi-giac-ngu\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more watches Smart with sleep tracking function at Mobile World\">sleep tracking</a> regularly, Galaxy Fit 3 turns rest into a fun and rewarding journey. The built-in <strong>Sleep Coach</strong> will help you optimize your sleep time, leaving you refreshed and energized every time you wake up.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your sleep will be illustrated with funny mascots, creating excitement and motivating you to improve your sleep quality. Each mascot represents a different sleep state, helping you easily monitor and adjust your sleeping habits accordingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Fit3 also has the ability to record snoring sounds while sleeping, helping you become aware of the problem and find solutions to improve it. Thanks to that, you can aim for a more complete and healthier sleep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this generation, Samsung has integrated additional features <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh?g=do-nong-do-oxy-trong-mau -spo2\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more SpO2 meters for sale at thegioididong.com\">measure blood oxygen concentration</a> (SpO2) for your device. With just a simple operation, you can know what your blood oxygen index is anytime, anywhere. This feature is especially useful for people who regularly practice intense sports, people with respiratory or cardiovascular problems, or people who live in high altitude environments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, Samsung Galaxy Fit 3 also supports many other common health features such as measuring heart rate, measuring stress levels, monitoring women&#39;s cycles,... Through these features you can can take care of your health more effectively and safely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-4.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Theo dõi sức khỏe\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-4.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Theo dõi sức khỏe\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Long battery life, companion in many activities</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Fit3 is equipped with a battery capacity of <strong>208 mAh </strong>which provides an impressive usage time of up to <strong>13 days</strong>. This number helps you feel completely secure in using the device on business trips or traveling away from home without worrying about battery charging interruptions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-samsung?g=vong-tay-thong-minh\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more Samsung smartbands at Mobile World\">Samsung smart bracelet</a> is equipped with a<strong> 5 ATM water resistance index</strong>. Therefore, you can comfortably wear the smart bracelet when going in the rain, washing hands, operating in shallow water,... without worrying about water getting inside, affecting the durability and functions of the device. suffered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-6.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Pin lên đến 13 ngày\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-6.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Pin lên đến 13 ngày\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Stable connection, receive notifications quickly</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Fit3 is equipped with advanced <strong>Bluetooth v5.3 </strong>technology, providing stable and fast connection with your smartphone. After successfully connecting, Galaxy Fit 3 will synchronize and display call notifications, messages and popular applications such as Zalo, Messenger, Viber, WhatsApp, Line,... right on your wrist. Thanks to that, you can update all important information quickly and conveniently without having to operate directly on <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank \" title=\"Refer to business phones at Mobile World\">phone</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Download the <strong>Galaxy Wearable</strong> app: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.android.app.watchmanager&amp;hl=en&amp;gl =US\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Download Galaxy Wearable app on CH Play\">Download link on CH Play</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-7.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Kết nối\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-7.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-7.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Kết nối\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Diverse user support utilities</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the main health and sports functions, Galaxy Fit3 is also equipped with many other smart utilities, providing a convenient and comfortable user experience such as: Music playback control, always-on display, find phone, find watch, fall warning, make SOS calls or SOS messages with location,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-8.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Tiện ích khác\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-8.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/321616/samsung-galaxy-fit3-slider-8.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Fit3 - Tiện ích khác\" /></a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-fit3-smart-bracelet', '2024-12-09 17:34:47', '2024-12-09 17:34:47', NULL),
