(120, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G tablet', NULL, '<h3>Samsung has launched a tablet model called <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-4g\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4 tablet at Mobile World\">Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G</a>, outstanding features of the device include good configuration in the price range, large screen and 5100 mAh battery integrated inside. This improves productivity while maintaining optimal mobility.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Flat, modern design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When looking at the Galaxy Tab A9 4G, the first thing users can feel is elegance and sophistication. Inspired by the flat design style, the screen and back of the product are perfectly similar to each other, creating a uniform and modern look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The back of the Galaxy Tab A9 4G is made of metal material, creating a classy and luxurious appearance. This material not only demonstrates sturdiness, but also helps dissipate heat effectively, ensuring that the device always operates stably and cool during use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103947.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Thiết kế máy tính bảng - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103947.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103947.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế máy tính bảng - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The special thing is the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-samsung\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung tablets at Mobile World This \">Samsung tablet</a> is designed in one piece, from the back to the frame. This not only increases uniformity but also enhances the rigidity and durability of the device. You can feel the care that went into the manufacturing process as both the front and back are harmonious and seamless, creating a truly beautiful and performing product.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Large screen with energy-saving technology</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The screen of the Galaxy Tab A9 4G is a bright spot in the product&#39;s design. Using TFT LCD screen technology is a smart choice, helping to save costs while still providing an attractive experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TFT LCD technology allows the screen to display clear images and good contrast, creating favorable conditions for watching movies, reading e-books and performing daily tasks. Screens with this technology also save energy, helping to extend the usage time of the device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the big impressions about <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to tablets at Mobile World\">tablet</a> is the large size of the screen up to 8.7 inches. This spacious screen creates a comfortable and expansive space, especially when you watch movies or browse the web.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103949.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Kích thước màn hình - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103949.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103949.jpg\" title=\"Kích thước màn hình - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is an important strength, allowing users to enjoy an immersive experience and make the most of the display space on the screen to interact with applications easily.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The screen of the Galaxy Tab A9 4G has high resolution with 800 x 1340 pixels. This ensures that the image on the screen is displayed clearly. Whether you&#39;re viewing photos, videos, or browsing the web, every detail on the screen appears realistic and vivid.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Supports clear shooting</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The rear camera of the Galaxy Tab A9 4G has a resolution of 8 MP, allowing users to take photos with good details and quite bright colors. Whether you are a photography lover or want to preserve special moments, this camera will satisfy you well on a basic level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The tablet camera is suitable for capturing beautiful everyday scenes around you or documents for work or study. Especially in environments with lots of light, the camera promises to deliver sharp and clear photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The front camera with 2 MP resolution is also a necessity for recording selfies and video calls. This level of resolution is just enough to create clear and easy-to-see video chats, allowing you to conveniently connect with friends and relatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103951.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Camera máy tính bảng - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103951.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/315390/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-251023-103951.jpg\" title=\"Camera máy tính bảng - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Full HD video recording ability of the rear camera, you can simply preserve memorable moments. Whether it&#39;s family parties, children&#39;s performances, or beautiful scenes in nature, the Galaxy Tab A9 4G will help you capture every detail with fine resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Uses MediaTek chipset</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Tab A9 4G is an impressive product, not only because of its appearance design but also because of its powerful performance. Powered by the Helio G99 chip, this device performs basic tasks quickly and efficiently. Whether you&#39;re browsing the web, watching videos, or using everyday apps, the Galaxy Tab A9 4G always responds quickly, providing a smooth and uninterrupted experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/317621/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-4g-cpu.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiệu năng - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/317621/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-4g-cpu.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/317621/samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-4g-cpu.jpg\" title=\"Hiệu năng - Samsung Galaxy Tab A9 4G\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sample <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-ram-4gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to 4 Gb RAM tablet at Di Gioi Di Dynamic\">4 GB RAM tablet</a>, the device is capable enough to multitask for light applications without experiencing lag or slowdown. Even when you open your email, browser, or social apps, the Galaxy Tab A9 4G always ensures you can switch between them easily, never having to wait too long due to any interruptions .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, with 64 GB of storage memory, users do not need to worry about storing too much data and files. However, if you need more space, you can also expand it by 1 TB via Micro SD card. This means that the device can store hundreds of videos, thousands of photos and thousands of files without having to worry about memory space.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-tab-a9-4g-tablet', '2024-12-09 17:40:31', '2024-12-09 17:40:31', NULL),
(119, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G tablet', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra at Thegioididong.com\">Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra</a> is a testament to the perfect combination of design, performance and smart features, providing an unprecedented user experience. This product is not simply a tablet, but also a powerful support tool for work, creativity and entertainment.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Exquisite and luxurious design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The design of the Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G is a breakthrough in both style and quality, with every detail meticulously completed to create a product that is both durable and attractive. The device has an extremely durable Armor Aluminum frame that increases impact and scratch resistance, while minimizing weight to provide a light and comfortable grip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-thiet-ke-638641572788242886.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Vẻ ngoài\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-thiet-ke-638641572788242886.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-thiet-ke-638641572788242886.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Vẻ ngoài\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can choose between two elegant tones: Moonstone Gray and Platinum Silver, both corresponding to the color of the included S Pen. This synchronization not only creates a harmonious appearance but also affirms the distinct class of the Tab S10 Ultra line. The included new generation S Pen has also been redesigned with an elegant design, increasing convenience, helping you unleash your creativity with greater precision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-mau-sac-638641580732562624.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Màu sắc\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-mau-sac-638641580732562624.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-mau-sac-638641580732562624.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Màu sắc\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With IP68 water and dust resistance standard, Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra can withstand environmental impacts such as water and dust. This helps you feel more secure when using the device in harsh conditions, providing maximum protection for your device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-ip68-638641581517025182.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Kháng nước\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-ip68-638641581517025182.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-ip68-638641581517025182.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Kháng nước\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Large screen, excellent display quality</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra has a 14.6-inch screen with Dynamic AMOLED 2X technology, providing sharp, brilliant and realistic display. The screen reaches a resolution of 1848 x 2960 pixels, displaying the smallest details vividly and clearly. With a 120 Hz refresh rate, every movement on the screen becomes extremely smooth, from surfing the web, playing games to sketching on the S Pen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-man-hinh-638641572780315313.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Màn hình\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-man-hinh-638641572780315313.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-man-hinh-638641572780315313.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Màn hình\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The screen has an Anti-reflection layer that helps minimize reflected light, improving visibility even under strong light. Meanwhile, the Vision Booster feature automatically adjusts the brightness and color of the screen based on the surrounding environment, helping to protect users&#39; eyes and ensure the best image quality in all lighting conditions.&lt; /p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Powerful performance with MediaTek chipset</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra is equipped with Dimensity 9300+ processor, providing outstanding powerful performance. Compared to the previous product line, it is <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/samsung-galaxy-tab-s9-ultra\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra at Thegioididong.com\">Samsung Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra</a>, this new chip has outstanding power when increasing CPU performance up to 18%, GPU up to 28% and NPU (single) (artificial intelligence processing position) increased by 14%. This upgrade helps the device smoothly handle high-end graphics tasks, video rendering or heavy gaming, while also optimizing energy usage to provide a long-lasting experience without worrying about overheating.&lt; /p&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-game-638641583243816906.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Game\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-game-638641583243816906.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-game-638641583243816906.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Game\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 12 GB RAM, Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra handles multitasking smoothly, allowing multiple applications to be opened at the same time without lag. 256 GB internal memory provides ample storage space for creative projects, 4K video, and heavy applications. If needed, you can expand memory via Micro SD card, ensuring comfortable storage without worrying about running out of space.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Experience Galaxy AI optimized for the big screen</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Special highlights of the phone <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-samsung\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Samsung tablets at Thegioididong.com This \">Samsung tablet</a> is smart features optimized by Galaxy AI. This is a completely new artificial intelligence platform, developed to bring maximum flexibility and convenience to users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the powerful Note assistant, this feature allows you to record meetings, convert audio directly to text, and even automatically format and summarize notes neatly. You won&#39;t need to worry about missing any information when participating in long meetings or seminars.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Translate directly from PDF files, now you no longer have problems accessing foreign documents. The direct translation feature helps readers understand PDF content immediately. The translation will be overlaid directly on the original text, making it easy for you to follow and compare without having to convert many times.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Circle feature to search with Google. Now, finding information becomes faster and more intuitive. You just need to circle or click on any image or text to get search results on Google. Galaxy AI also supports instant translation, meeting your multilingual learning and working needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-khoanh-tron-638641585868693914.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Khoanh tròn tìm kiếm\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-khoanh-tron-638641585868693914.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-khoanh-tron-638641585868693914.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Khoanh tròn tìm kiếm\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Smart Sketch: This feature allows you to create creative drawings from simple sketches or doodles. The combination of the S Pen and AI will help turn primitive ideas into sophisticated works of art, suitable for designers or people who love drawing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-phac-thao-638641585880164072.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Phác hoạ\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-phac-thao-638641585880164072.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-phac-thao-638641585880164072.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Phác hoạ\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Versatile camera with excellent recording capabilities</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra is equipped with a rear camera cluster including a 13 MP main camera and an 8 MP ultra wide-angle camera, helping you take sharp, realistic photos and videos. 12 MP front camera with 12 MP super wide-angle secondary camera, good support for video calls and selfies. Thanks to that, you always appear with the best image during conference calls or snapshots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-camera-truoc-638641572762808749.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Camera trước\" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-camera-truoc-638641572762808749.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/522/322132/samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-camera-truoc-638641572762808749.jpg\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Tab S10 Ultra 5G 256GB - Camera trước\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compared to the Galaxy Tab S9 Ultra series, the Tab S10 Ultra&#39;s camera system has been upgraded to provide better image and video capture capabilities, ensuring display quality even in poor lighting conditions.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'samsung-galaxy-tab-s10-ultra-5g-tablet', '2024-12-09 17:40:39', '2024-12-09 17:40:39', NULL),
(118, 2, 'OPPO Pad Neo WiFi tablet', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/oppo-pad-neo-6gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to OPPO Pad Neo WiFi at Mobile World Dynamic\">OPPO Pad Neo WiFi</a>, a new version from OPPO that brings a difference in the tablet market. With an 11.4-inch wide screen, stable chip and large RAM help it attract attention, giving users a smooth and durable experience.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Flat shape combined with high-quality materials</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Pad Neo WiFi has a back design made from high-quality glass and aluminum, providing high durability as well as sophistication and elegance. When light shines on, this back surface reflects back, creating strange light effects that help bring a more interesting look to the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That&#39;s just the back, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi continues to attract attention with its curved frame made from metal, providing an overall harmony between softness and rigidity. With an impressive thinness of only 6.89 mm, this tablet not only serves as a useful tool but also a symbol of sophistication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-1-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-1-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-1-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Thiết kế hiện đại cao cấp - OPPO Pad Neo\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With an 11.4-inch screen and a length of 255.12 mm, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi not only helps improve the entertainment experience, but is also suitable for daily tasks. The large size of the screen not only enhances aesthetics but also increases elegance, the perfect choice to show the class of a high-end product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the same time, the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-oppo\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to OPPO tablets at Mobile World\">OPPO tablet</a