ing the device into a reliable working tool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-4-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-4-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-4-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ các tính năng bảo vệ mắt - OPPO Pad Neo\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>But not only about image quality, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi also has smart features with a color temperature sensor. It allows users to customize the color temperature of the screen to suit lighting conditions and personal vision, helping to prevent eyes from getting tired after long periods of use.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Equiped with 8 MP front and rear cameras</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>OPPO Pad Neo WiFi&#39;s front camera has 8 MP resolution, allowing you to make high-quality, sharp video calls, without any blur or blur. This is extremely useful when you need to participate in an online meeting or want to connect with loved ones via video call even though you are far away.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-5-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-5-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-5-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp camera 8 MP - OPPO Pad Neo\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with an 8 MP rear camera, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi also helps you capture work documents with high clarity and detail. From here, the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to tablets at Mobile World\"> OPPO</a>&#39;s tablet is not only a means of entertainment but also becomes a powerful partner in your work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Full HD video recording ability of the rear camera is one of the highlights of OPPO Pad Neo WiFi. This makes it easy to capture special moments, from family gatherings to peaceful scenes of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Configuration is powerful enough for basic tasks</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With the MediaTek Helio G99 chip, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi is not a product aimed at fast operating speed or huge capacity. In return, it is a useful tool that provides exactly what users need from web browsing, text editing to stable online meetings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-6-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-6-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-6-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Cấu hình ổn trong tầm giá - OPPO Pad Neo\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even though it is not a masterpiece for gamers, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi is still capable of conquering some games that are not too heavy, turning the device into a diverse entertainment device, thereby creating opportunities for gamers. Users can experience and enjoy relaxing moments after stressful working hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-7-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-7-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-7-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ RAM lên đến 8 GB - OPPO Pad Neo\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides, this is the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-ram-6gb\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference 6 GB RAM tablet at Mobile World\">6 GB RAM tablet</a>, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi promises not to let users face interruptions or delays, allowing users Easily switch between applications Use smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Integrated huge battery up to 8000 mAh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Possessing a huge capacity of 8000 mAh, the device is the ideal choice for those who want to enjoy entertainment, do work or study for many hours. With high capacity, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi provides a long day of use without worrying too much about charging time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And yet, not only focusing on battery capacity, OPPO also especially focuses on improving the fast charging ability of its devices. The 33 W fast charging technology integrated in OPPO Pad Neo WiFi creates fast charging capabilities, helping users save time to the maximum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-8-1020x570.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-8-1020x570.jpg\" height=\"570\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/522/320992/oppo-pad-neo-8-1020x570.jpg\" title=\"Trang bị viên pin lớn và có sạc nhanh - OPPO Pad Neo\" width=\"1020\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In summary, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi is a product that the company has prepared meticulously from all aspects. Thanks to that, OPPO Pad Neo WiFi has the ability to cope strongly with basic to advanced office work needs, while supporting quick and easy document lookup during the user&#39;s learning process. .</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'oppo-pad-neo-wifi-tablet', '2024-12-09 17:40:47', '2024-12-09 17:40:47', NULL),
