rc=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032428.jpg\" title=\"Màn hình chất lượng - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comes with a large screen with a resolution of up to 1200 x 2000 Pixels, so the content I watch is reproduced with high detail and clarity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I gave the device to parents to try, then I received very positive feedback about the screen because it helps people see the content much more clearly than on phones. usually.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032430.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiển thị văn bản rõ ràng - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032430.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032430.jpg\" title=\"Hiển thị văn bản rõ ràng - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, I received a few comments that the text on the screen is quite small, so reading the newspaper is a bit difficult, but I fixed this immediately because the device supports change mode. Change the font size with many different levels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032432.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hỗ trợ điều chỉnh kích thước - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032432.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032432.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ điều chỉnh kích thước - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The device supports a split-screen feature that allows you to use two applications at the same time, which is really useful for those who both study online and take notes on the same device. suffered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032434.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tích hợp tính năng chia đôi màn hình - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032434.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032434.jpg\" title=\"Tích hợp tính năng chia đôi màn hình - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For office workers like me, this is truly an extremely necessary feature on a personal tablet. It helps me read documents and monitor online meetings at the same time. convenient.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This time OPPO equips this tablet with an IPS LCD panel, this is considered a screen technology that produces quite realistic colors and high brightness. In addition, the company also said that this screen supports 1 billion colors, which is truly what every content and image creator looks forward to on a mid-range tablet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032436.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Tái hiện màu sắc trung thực - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032436.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032436.jpg\" title=\"Tái hiện màu sắc trung thực - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In order to verify the reliability of accurate color reproduction, I also compared the image displayed on OPPO Pad Air with a screen with higher color accuracy. The result I see is that both screens produce colors that are quite similar to each other, really not too different, so I feel more secure in designing content for printing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Powerful performance comes from Qualcomm chip</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This time OPPO equipped the Snapdragon 680 chip on its latest tablet, which is considered a national chip commonly found on mid-range smartphones on the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032437.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hiệu năng mạnh mẽ - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032437.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032437.jpg\" title=\"Hiệu năng mạnh mẽ - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The reputation of stability on the chip has also been verified through many previous product lines equipped with this processor, so I also feel more secure in choosing the device as the main device. to serve all tasks for a period of experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the needs of surfing the web, watching movies, and listening to music, OPPO Pad Air almost did not encounter any difficulties while using it. Along with that is the optimization of the software on the Android 12 operating system so everything runs smoothly, the application opening speed is quite fast so I am also very satisfied.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032439.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Hỗ trợ Android 12 - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032439.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032439.jpg\" title=\"Hỗ trợ Android 12 - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next is the game test on OPPO Pad Air, the highest graphics level that the device can support on Lien Quan is &quot;High&quot;. Although the image output is not excellent, it compensates for its long-term stability. The frame rate I measured is at 60 FPS, and lag also rarely occurs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032441.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Bảng đo tốc độ khung hình - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032441.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032441.jpg\" title=\"Bảng đo tốc độ khung hình - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And in the game PUBG Mobile, which has smooth graphics settings and extremely high frame rates, the FPS score I measured fluctuated around 29.8. In my opinion, the device can only support play at a relative level, but if you use the device to serve leveling, this is not really the optimal choice because lag still occurs. quite a lot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032443.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Bảng đo tốc độ khung hình - OPPO Pad Air\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032443.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/281821/oppo-pad-air-260822-032443.jpg\" title=\"Bảng đo tốc độ khung hình - OPPO Pad Air\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s a <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-ram-4gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to 4 GB RAM tablet at The World Mobile\">4 GB RAM tablet</a> with the ability to expand an additional 3 GB, so multitasking with multiple applications at the same time can also operate quite smoothly. I have multiple Chrome tabs open at the same time, but reloading the page from the beginning rarely happens, it helps me work as efficiently and quickly as on a laptop.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'oppo-pad-air-wifi-tablet', '2024-12-09 17:40:56', '2024-12-09 17:40:56', NULL),
