(115, 2, 'iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi Tablet', NULL, '<h3>Possesses a trendy design with optimized thinness, high-quality dual-layer OLED technology, and powerful performance from the new generation Apple chip, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong .com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB tablet for sale at Di Gioi Di Dynamic \">iPad Pro M4 13 inch 512GB</a> will be an excellent choice for users who love technology and need a versatile device for both work and entertainment, especially in the field of creativity. create, design.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Apple&#39;s thinnest tablet</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPad Pro M4 13 inch 512GB stands out with an ultra-thin design of only 5.1 mm, becoming one of Apple&#39;s thinnest products ever. This design not only brings a sophisticated and modern appearance, but also helps users have a more comfortable usage experience when it can be stowed in a backpack or handbag to carry anywhere, anytime without spending too much. space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The chassis is finished from solid aluminum with 4 soft curved edges, creating a seamless, trendy Apple-like beauty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-8.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Thiết kế \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-8.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-8.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Thiết kế \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When using iPad with <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/phu-kien-thong-minh/apple-pencil-pro\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Apple Pencil Pro at Thegioididong.com\">Apple Pencil Pro</a> newly launched by the Apple family, you can unleash your creativity, draw, take notes,... with each gesture vividly reproduced. The pen has perfect precision down to each pixel, low latency, tilt sensitivity, and also supports palm rest, enhancing the entertainment and working experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i>Note: Apple Pencil Pro is sold separately.</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-6.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Apple Pencil Pro \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-6.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Apple Pencil Pro \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Super vivid Ultra Retina XDR display</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-apple-ipad-pro-m4\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the iPad Pro M4 line at Thegioididong. com\">iPad Pro M4</a> features a 13-inch Ultra Retina XDR display, using dual-layer OLED technology, providing up to 1000 nits of full-screen brightness and 1600 nits when displaying HDR content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High contrast ratio of 2,000,000:1 and resolution of 2064 x 2752 pixels provide the ability to display deep blacks and vivid details. Supporting technologies such as True Tone and ProMotion also help adjust color and scanning frequency flexibly, providing a great visual experience for users who create content or design graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-4.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Màn hình Ultra Retina XDR \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-4.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Màn hình Ultra Retina XDR \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Top powerful processor</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Apple M4 chip on iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB is designed based on the 2nd generation 3 nm process, with 9-core CPU and 10-core GPU providing 1.5 times faster performance, graphics performance 4 times more powerful than the previous generation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, the improved Neural Engine also helps speed up AI processing and machine learning, supporting smart features of iPadOS such as image lookup, live text capture, and AI-based notes. This outstanding performance makes it the ideal tool for tasks ranging from office work to multimedia entertainment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-5.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Chip M4\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-5.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Chip M4\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>8 GB RAM satisfies the need to multitask multiple applications at the same time without experiencing lag or freezing. 512 GB ROM gives you enough storage space for applications, creative works, videos, design images or documents,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For users who need more memory, Apple also offers versions with higher storage capacity such as <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh -bang/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-1tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 1TB Tablet\">iPad Pro M4 13 inch 1TB</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-2tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Machine iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 2TB tablet\">iPad Pro M4 13 inch 2TB</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-2.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - RAM 8 GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-2.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - RAM 8 GB\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Professional camera system</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business tablets at Thegioididong.com\">Tablet<!-- a--> is equipped with an Ultra Wide front camera and a Wide rear camera both with 12 MP resolution, helping you conveniently perform photography and video calling tasks with clear quality down to every detail. </a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business tablets at Thegioididong.com\">In addition, the iPad&#39;s rear camera also supports recording movies with resolution up to 4K, ProRes video to best compress your video quality, and take vivid Smart HDR photos with more vibrant colors. , detail in low light conditions is also improved.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business tablets at Thegioididong.com\">Apple has moved the front camera position to the long edge of the iPad, providing more convenience for users when placing the device in landscape mode. This camera also helps you quickly unlock iPad with Face ID, in addition to improving the security of data and personal images on the device.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to business tablets at Thegioididong.com\">In addition, the company also offers users Center Stage technology, with the ability to move the frame according to your gestures, ensuring you are always the focus of the frame during video calls and online meetings. ,...</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-1.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Camera\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325518/ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-512gb-bv-1.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 13 inch WiFi 512GB - Camera\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The battery lasts</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The battery has a performance of 38.99 Wh of <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-apple-ipad\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to the tablet line iPad at Thegioididong.com\">iPad</a> provides up to about 10 hours of use when using a Wi-Fi connection when surfing the web or watching videos, meeting the needs of continuous use during a full day of work or study without needing to recharge midway. This is a big plus, especially for those who often travel and need a device that can last all day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brings outstanding performance from the Apple M4 chip, ultra-thin and light design, multi-utility camera system, quality speakers and mic, spacious 13-inch screen with vivid, sharp 2-layer OLED technology down to every detail... iPad Pro M4 13 inch 512GB will be the perfect companion for all the needs of graphic design, photo editing, video rendering,... of creative users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For a more perfect sound experience, you can choose to purchase the included version <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-mxp63\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 headphones at Thegioididong.com\">Latest AirPods 4</a> from Apple. Combining iPad and AirPods 4 will bring vivid sound, especially with version <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tai-nghe/airpods-4-chong-on-mxp93\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to AirPods 4 ANC at Thegioididong.com\">AirPods 4 ANC</a> active noise cancellation, helping you immerse yourself in your own space fourth.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ipad-pro-m4-13-inch-wifi-tablet', '2024-12-09 17:41:13', '2024-12-09 17:41:13', NULL);
