(114, 2, 'iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G tablet', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Reference iPad Pro M4 Cellular 256GB at Thegioididong.com\">iPad Pro M4 Cellular</a>, the top tablet model of 2024, offers outstanding performance thanks to the Apple M4 chip, screen Sharp Ultra Retina XDR image and front camera placed on the long side for convenience. With a thin, light design and impressive battery life, iPad Pro M4 Cellular promises to be the ideal choice for technology enthusiasts.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Slim, lighter, more advanced design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The frame of the iPad Pro M4 Cellular is designed to be flat and square, providing a solid and durable feeling when held in the hand. This design not only creates an aesthetic highlight but also reflects professionalism and elegance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-frame-vien.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Khung viền\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-khung-vien.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-khung-vien.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Khung viền\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The corners on iPad Pro M4 Cellular are gently rounded, making it more comfortable to hold, especially when used for long periods of time. The unibody aluminum body not only provides a smooth look but also enhances the device&#39;s durability and premium feel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a thickness of 5.3 mm and a weight of only 446 g, iPad Pro M4 Cellular shines as one of the thinnest and lightest tablets today. This proves that Apple always focuses on optimizing size, bringing maximum comfort to users while still maintaining strong performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-do-mong.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Độ mỏng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-do-mong.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-do-mong.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Độ mỏng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/phu-kien-thong-minh/apple-pencil-pro\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to Apple Pencil Pro at Thegioididong.com\">Apple Pencil Pro</a> is equipped with haptic feedback technology, allowing users to feel each stroke and take notes with precision and sensitivity. This feature realistically reproduces every movement, from smooth strokes to precise strokes. With pressure detection, users can create light and dark lines naturally, just like using real pen and paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i>Note: Apple Pencil Pro is an accessory purchased separately.</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-pencil.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Bút Apple Pencil Pro\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-pencil.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-pencil.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Bút Apple Pencil Pro\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Detailed, sharp display</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Possessing Ultra Retina XDR technology, the iPad Pro M4 Cellular screen pioneers advanced 2-layer OLED technology. This combination allows the screen to achieve extremely high contrast, with deeper blacks and brighter whites than conventional OLED screens.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-man-hinh.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Màn hình\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-man-hinh.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-man-hinh.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Màn hình\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With an 11-inch wide screen, iPad Pro M4 Cellular provides spacious display space, enough to show the smallest details. The resolution of 1668 x 2420 pixels, much higher than conventional standards, makes every image, from text to complex graphics, clear and sharp in every detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adaptive scanning frequency from 10-120 Hz helps the iPad Pro M4 Cellular screen adjust the refresh rate to suit each content, increasing the experience of watching movies and playing games smoothly while saving energy. 1600 nits brightness when displaying HDR content helps the screen stand out, ensuring true HDR display under all lighting conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Breakthrough performance with Apple M4 chipset</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>iPad Pro M4 Cellular is equipped with the Apple M4 chipset, a breakthrough with architecture based on second generation 3 nm technology. This technology significantly improves operating performance while maintaining energy efficiency. This means that not only daily tasks run smoothly, but also applications that require high processing power such as graphics and video processing do not encounter any problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-m4.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Hiệu năng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-m4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-m4.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Hiệu năng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a 9-core CPU and 10-core GPU, iPad Pro M4 Cellular is designed to provide powerful graphics performance. This allows the device to tackle a wide range of graphics challenges, from rendering games with high-end graphics to quickly exporting complex projects in video editing applications like Final Cut Pro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-trai-nghiem.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Trải nghiệm hiệu năng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-trai-nghiem.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-trai-nghiem.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Trải nghiệm hiệu năng\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M4&#39;s Neural Engine is capable of processing up to 38 trillion operations per second, helping improve the performance of AI-powered applications, making them smarter, more responsive and more efficient. more effective. With this capability, users can perform tasks such as separating objects in videos with just one touch in Final Cut Pro, among many other benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-apple-ipad-pro-m4\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPad Pro M4 at Thegioididong.com This \">iPad Pro M4</a> supports 8 GB RAM, providing enough capacity for efficient multitasking, helping you perform multiple tasks and open heavy applications without worrying about lag. 256 GB internal memory ensures you have enough storage space, no need to worry about running out of space for data or applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See more: <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-512gb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPad Pro M4 Cellular 512GB at Thegioididong.com\">iPad Pro M4 Cellular 512GB</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-1tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPad Pro M4 Cellular 1TB at Thegioididong.com\">iPad Pro M4 Cellular 1TB</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-2tb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refer to iPad Pro M4 Cellular 2TB at Thegioididong.com\">iPad Pro M4 Cellular 2TB</a> at Mobile World.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iPadOS 17 on iPad Pro M4 Cellular takes advantage of M4&#39;s accelerated machine learning, bringing new features and interface improvements, making it smoother and more intuitive to use. Especially, in professional work processes that require accuracy and speed, iPad Pro M4 Cellular clearly demonstrates its advantages.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Upgraded camera, improved quality</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The iPad Pro M4 Cellular&#39;s 12 MP rear camera provides premium Smart HDR 4 image quality, automatically adjusting to extract the finest detail from the landscape. Thanks to that, the captured images become vivid and rich in color, even in low light conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-camera.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Camera\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-camera.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/325529/ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-wifi-cellular-256gb-camera.jpg\" title=\"iPad Pro M4 11 inch 5G 256GB - Camera\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4K video recording on the iPad Pro M4 Cellular is truly a significant highlight for those working professionally in the video field. This capability not only delivers sharp video quality, but also helps add professionalism and smoothness to the editing and content production process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The iPad Pro M4 Cellular&#39;s 12 MP Ultra Wide front camera is newly designed, moving from the top edge to the long edge of the device, creating an ideal position when using the device horizontally. This is great for meetings, online learning, and video calls. With the Center Stage feature that automatically adjusts the frame to keep users centered, even when they move, providing a natural online experience.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ipad-pro-m4-11-inch-5g-tablet', '2024-12-09 17:41:22', '2024-12-09 17:41:22', NULL),
