(100, 2, 'Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm smartwatch', NULL, '<h3><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-rubber\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm Titanium border rubber band\">Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm Titanium border rubber band</a> is a convergence of classy style level and advanced technology. Attractive design with outstanding durability, this watch model is not only a fashion device but also a useful health support tool. With the ability to measure electrocardiogram (ECG), monitor sleep, provide rich exercise modes,... the watch helps you easily control your health and adjust your lifestyle. GT 5 Pro&#39;s battery can last up to 14 days, bringing convenience to users without having to charge frequently.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Exquisite design and outstanding durability</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-huawei-watch-gt-5-pro\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more Smart Watches Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro at Mobile World \">Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro smartwatch</a> has a premium and durable design with a high-quality Titanium alloy frame, giving it a luxurious look that Still ensuring lightness and comfort comfortable when worn. The rotating button is exquisitely decorated with a prominent red border, creating a classic and luxurious highlight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This material is not only scratch-resistant but also corrosion-resistant, helping to keep the watch shiny over time. The watch face has sharp machined edges, creating a strong, masculine and attractive feeling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using transparent, highly durable Sapphire glass, the watch screen is protected from impacts and chemical impacts, helping the watch maintain its new-like beauty over time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The soft rubber strap is also a big plus, especially suitable for people with sensitive skin, does not cause irritation and feels comfortable when worn all day long.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro is equipped with a sharp 1.43-inch AMOLED screen, displaying vivid images, high contrast and realistic colors, helping users easily read information on the screen in many situations. different lighting conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The watch also offers many customizable skins, allowing you to change according to your personal style or preferences. Always-On Display screen mode helps you easily monitor time and notifications quickly without complicated operations, creating convenience in daily life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day- rubber-2-638663277604058469.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Thiết kế \" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-2-638663277604058469.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-2-638663277604058469.jpg\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Thiết kế \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Modern health monitoring features</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-huawei\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more Huawei smart watches at Mobile World\">Huawei</a>&#39;s smart watch is also a great assistant in health care. With continuous heart rate measurement and early warning features, you can monitor your heart health more easily. The feature of measuring SpO2 and monitoring stress levels also helps users better understand their overall health status, thereby adjusting their lifestyle to maintain optimal health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced ECG measurement feature with electrode sensor technology helps accurately record electrical activity of the heart in 30 seconds, supporting the detection of signs of abnormal heart rhythm such as atrial fibrillation. The watch also analyzes and monitors your sleep quality, providing improvement recommendations to help you sleep better every night.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HUAWEI TruSense smart algorithm provides comprehensive health analysis data, from the respiratory system to the nervous system, helping you monitor your body in detail and build healthy self-care habits. study.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i>Note: Information on the watch is for reference only and cannot be used for diagnosis or treatment.</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day- rubber-4-638663277624739575.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Sức khỏe \" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-4-638663277624739575.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-4-638663277624739575.jpg\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Sức khỏe \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Flexible Personal Trainer</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-da-tien-ich\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more multi-utility smart watches business at Mobile World \">Multi-utility smartwatch</a> integrates more than 100 diverse training modes, meeting needs from basic exercises such as jogging, swimming, to gyms. Advanced subjects like rock climbing or yoga. Indicators such as heart rate, number of steps and calories consumed in each workout session are recorded in detail, helping you easily adjust and track your training progress.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Activity Ring 2.0 feature, the watch acts as a companion to help you stay motivated to exercise. Personalized challenges and goals help you pursue a healthy lifestyle and achieve your best fitness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day- rubber-5-638663277632778409.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Luyện tập \" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-5-638663277632778409.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-5-638663277632778409.jpg\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Luyện tập \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Precise positioning and advanced satellite technology</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>GT 5 Pro supports multi-satellite positioning system, including GPS, GLONASS, QZSS, Galileo and Beidou, combined with dual-band technology that allows you to quickly and accurately determine your location even in areas with weak signals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&#39;re climbing, jogging, or exploring new trails, precise positioning makes it easy to follow your route and find your way back, providing peace of mind when traveling outdoors. unfamiliar areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day- rubber-6-638663277641869559.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Định vị \" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-6-638663277641869559.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-6-638663277641869559.jpg\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Định vị \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Flexible connections and modern amenities</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With wide compatibility with Android and iOS operating systems, connecting via the Huawei Health application, this smartwatch will become your effective assistant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the quality speaker and microphone and stable Bluetooth v5.2 connection, you can comfortably talk right on your wrist. Besides, receiving notifications directly on the watch helps you not miss any important calls or messages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Download Huawei Health app at: <a href=\"https://appgallery.huawei.com/app/C10414141\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Download Huawei Health app on AppGallery\">AppGallery</a> (for Android) | <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/huawei-health/id1325481372?l=vi\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Download Huawei Health app on App Store\">App Store&lt; /a&gt; (for iOS)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day- rubber-3-638663277612710234.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Kết nối \" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-3-638663277612710234.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-3-638663277612710234.jpg\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Kết nối \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Water resistance and long battery life</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With 5 ATM ISO 22810:2010 water resistance standard, the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"See more copper smart watch business at The Gioi Di Dong \">your smart watch</a> will be the ideal companion for all water activities, from relaxing baths to swimming trips in the water shallow. However, to protect the device in the long term, it is necessary to limit operating the control buttons when in contact with water, and do not bring the device into saunas, hot tubs, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In terms of battery, GT 5 Pro can be used up to 14 days after just one full charge. When Always-On Display mode is turned on, the battery life still lasts about 5 days, meeting all daily needs as well as long-term travel and business trips without the need for frequent charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day- rubber-7-638663277650007472.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Pin và Chống nước \" data-src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-7-638663277650007472.jpg\" src=\"https://cdnv2.tgdd.vn/mwg-static/tgdd/Products/Images/7077/330173/huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-vien-titanium-day-cao-su-7-638663277650007472.jpg\" title=\"Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro 46mm viền Titanium dây cao su - Pin và Chống nước \" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Diverse utilities for modern life</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to health and sports monitoring features, Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro is also equipped with many useful utilities such as music control, stopwatch, weather, flashlight,... bringing convenience and flexibility for users in all situations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Huawei Watch GT 5 Pro with Titanium rim and rubber strap is the ideal choice for those looking for a product that is not only sophisticated in design but also powerful in health and sports support features. With accurate positioning capabilities, durable battery, flexible connectivity,... the device will be your reliable companion in your busy life. This is not only a smart watch but also a tool to help improve the health and healthy lifestyle of users.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'huawei-watch-gt-5-pro-46mm-smartwatch', '2024-12-09 17:43:38', '2024-12-09 17:43:38', NULL);
